[GG] Spellbook Prompt.code:
; NAME: [GG] Spellbook Prompt
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: Space|Destination
; PARAM: Space|NextSpace
; PARAM: Space|PreviousSpace

ADDIU SP SP -120
SW RA 116(SP)
SW S0 112(SP) ; Option Selection Index (usually)
SW S1 108(SP) ; Current Player Pages Value
SW S2 104(SP) ; Current Player Pages Address
SW S3 100(SP)
SW S4 96(SP) ; Current Player Struct
SW S5 92(SP)
SW S6 88(SP)
SW S7 84(SP)
SW FP 80(SP)



LI FP 0 ; No Protean Ace Internal Flag
; DELETE THIS AFTER TESTING
;LI T0 0x800cd096
;LI T1 0xA
;SB T1 0(T0)


firstprompt:
JAL RefreshOptionArray
NOP

JAL GetPlayerStruct ; at V0
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
MOVE S4 V0 ; Copy to S4

LI S5 0x800CD096 ; Page Count Address
LB T1 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index

ADDU S2 S5 T1 ; Add to get Current Player's Page Count Address
LBU S1 0(S2) ; Load Current Player's Page Count

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 A0 ; Shift Left by Player Index 

LUI T3 hi(0x800CD09D)
ADDIU T3 T3 lo(0x800CD09D) ; Liquidation Flag Address
LBU T4 0(T3) ; Flag Value

AND V0 T4 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Curse is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ V0 liquidationdrawback
NOP

LUI T3 hi(0x800CD09E)
ADDIU T3 T3 lo(0x800CD09E) ; Protean Ace Address
LBU T4 0(T3) ; Flag Value

AND V0 T4 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Curse is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ V0 proteanacedrawback
NOP

BNEZ FP lastproteancheck
NOP
BEQZ S1 cantusespells ; exit to check Magic Veil if current player has no Pages
NOP

JAL CheckMagicVeil
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index

BNEZ V0 cantusespells ; exit if Current Player can't use Spells
NOP

lastproteancheck:
JAL GetColorFormatter
NOP ; returns color for 2nd and 3rd option on V0, V1, and T0-2

LUI A0 hi(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(A_Pointer_with_enough_space) ; Parse Destination
LUI A1 hi(Spellbook_Prompt)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(Spellbook_Prompt) ; String Format
MOVE A2 V0 ; 1st Option Color
MOVE A3 V1 ; 2nd Option Color
SW T0 16(SP) ; 3rd Option Color
SW T1 20(SP) ; 4th Option Color
SW T2 24(SP) ; 5th Option Color
JAL sprintf ; Creates String 
SW R0 28(SP) ; Terminator

SW R0 16(SP)
SW R0 20(SP)
SW R0 24(SP)
LI A0 -1 ; (None)
LUI A1 hi(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
LI A2 0
JAL ShowMessage
LI A3 0

JAL DisableOptions ; A0 has Window ID
NOP

JAL GetAIChoice
NOP
SW V1 76(SP)

LI A0 2 ; Pick whatever is in A1 as AI's Choice
JAL GetBasicPromptSelection
MOVE A1 V0
MOVE S0 V0 ; Chosen answer at S0

JAL CloseMessage_Function
NOP

BEQZ S0 movementspell
NOP
LI T0 1
BEQ S0 T0 itemspell
NOP
LI T0 2
BEQ S0 T0 coinspell
NOP
LI T0 3
BEQ S0 T0 magicspell
NOP
LI T0 4
BEQ S0 T0 miscspell
NOP
LI T0 5
BEQ S0 T0 exit
NOP
JAL ViewBoardMap
NOP
J firstprompt
NOP



movementspell:
JAL GetColorFormatter_Movement
NOP ; returns color for 2nd and 3rd option on V0, V1, and T0-2

LUI A0 hi(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(A_Pointer_with_enough_space) ; Parse Destination
LUI A1 hi(Movement_Prompt)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(Movement_Prompt) ; String Format
MOVE A2 V0 ; 1st Option Color
MOVE A3 V1 ; 2nd Option Color
SW T0 16(SP) ; 3rd Option Color
JAL sprintf ; Creates String 
SW R0 20(SP) ; Terminator

SW R0 16(SP)
SW R0 20(SP)
SW R0 24(SP)
LI A0 -1 ; (None)
LUI A1 hi(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
LI A2 0
JAL ShowMessage
LI A3 0

JAL DisableOptions_3 ; A0 has Window ID
NOP

;JAL AIChoice_Autumn
NOP

LI A0 2 ; Pick whatever is in A1 as AI's Choice
JAL GetBasicPromptSelection
LI A1 2 ; Loaded Dice
MOVE S0 V0 ; Chosen answer at S0

JAL CloseMessage_Function
NOP

BEQZ S0 diceyjunctions
NOP
LI T0 1 
BEQ S0 T0 broomzoom
NOP
LI T0 2
BEQ S0 T0 loadeddice
NOP
LI T0 3
BEQ S0 T0 spellexplanations_movement
NOP
LI T0 4
BEQ S0 T0 firstprompt
NOP
JAL ViewBoardMap
NOP
J movementspell
NOP

;========================================================================================BROOM ZOOM
broomzoom:
SW R0 16(SP)
SW R0 20(SP)
SW R0 24(SP)
LI A0 -1 ; (None)
LUI A1 hi(BroomZoomSelection_Prompt)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(BroomZoomSelection_Prompt)
LI A2 0
JAL ShowMessage
LI A3 0

;JAL AIChoice_Autumn
NOP

LI A0 2 ; Pick whatever is in A1 as AI's Choice
JAL GetBasicPromptSelection
MOVE A1 V0
MOVE S0 V0 ; Chosen answer at S0

JAL CloseMessage_Function
NOP

SLTI T0 S0 4 ; ON IF Warp destination was chosen
BNEZ T0 broomzoomwarp
NOP
LI T0 4
BEQ S0 T0 movementspell
NOP
JAL ViewBoardMap
NOP
J broomzoom
NOP

broomzoomwarp:
BNEZ FP broomzoomwarpproteanskip
NOP 

LI T1 4
SUBU S1 S1 T1 ; Subtract 4 Pages
SB S1 0(S2) ; Store new number of Pages

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x1D1 ; Page Subtract Sound

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 30 ; Frames

broomzoomwarpproteanskip:
LI A0 0 ; Bar Code fade-out
JAL InitFadeOut
LI A1 16 ; 16 Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 16

JAL PlaySound 
LI A0 0x107 ; Warp Block Sound Index

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 20

LUI T0 hi(BroomZoomDestination_Array)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(BroomZoomDestination_Array)
ADDU T0 T0 S0 ; Add option index to array to get correct space index
LBU S7 0(T0) ; Load Index to S7

JAL GetChainAndSpaceIndexFromAbsSpaceIndex 
LBU A0 0(T0) 

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Player's Index
MOVE A1 V0 ; Chain Index
JAL SetPlayerOntoChain
MOVE A2 V1 ; Chain Space Index

LUI T0 hi(BroomZoomNext_Array)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(BroomZoomNext_Array)
ADDU T0 T0 S0 ; Add option index to array to get correct space index

JAL GetChainAndSpaceIndexFromAbsSpaceIndex 
LBU A0 0(T0) 

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Player's Index
MOVE A1 V0 ; Chain Index
JAL SetNextChainAndSpace
MOVE A2 V1 ; Chain Space Index

LUI T0 hi(BroomZoomPrevious_Array)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(BroomZoomPrevious_Array)
ADDU T0 T0 S0 ; Add option index to array to get correct space index

JAL GetChainAndSpaceIndexFromAbsSpaceIndex 
LBU A0 0(T0) 

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Player's Index
MOVE A1 V0 ; Chain Index
JAL SetPrevChainAndSpace
MOVE A2 V1 ; Chain Space Index

JAL GetSpaceData
MOVE A0 S7 ; Space Index

ADDIU V0 V0 8 ; This gets the X pos of the space
LW V1 0(V0) 
MOVE T0 V1 ; Copy to T0

ADDIU V0 V0 8 ; This gets the Y pos of the space
LW V1 0(V0)
MOVE T1 V1 ; Copy to T1

LI T2 0x41200000 ; Float value for 10
MTC1 T2 F0 ; Move Float to F0
MTC1 T1 F1 ; Move Space Y Pos float to F1
ADD.S F0 F0 F1 ; Add the floats for maximum floatiness
MFC1 T1 F0 ; Move total to T1

LW V1 0x24(S4) ; Load Offset 24 into V1
ADDIU V1 V1 0xC ; Add 0xC to get current player's X Coords
SW T0 0(V1) 

ADDIU V1 V1 8 ; This should load current player's Y Coords
SW T1 0(V1)

JAL PlaySound 
LI A0 0x107 ; Warp Block Sound Index

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 15

LI A0 0 ; Bar Code fade-in
JAL InitFadeIn
LI A1 16 ; 16 Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 31

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 A0 ; Shift Left by Player Index 

LUI T3 hi(0x800CD0AF)
ADDIU T3 T3 lo(0x800CD0AF) ; Cursed Dice Flag Address
LBU T4 0(T3) ; Flag Value

AND V0 T4 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Curse is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ V0 flipitemuseflag
NOP

ADDU T4 T4 T2 ; Add to get new flag value
SB T4 0(T3) ; Store new flag

J flipitemuseflag
NOP

;===================================================================================DICEY JUNCTIONS

diceyjunctions:
JAL GetColorFormatter_Dicey ; in T1, T3, T4, and T5 
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Pass Current Player's Index

LUI A0 hi(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(A_Pointer_with_enough_space) ; Parse Destination
LUI A1 hi(DiceyJunctions_Prompt)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(DiceyJunctions_Prompt) ; String Format
MOVE A2 V0 ; P1 Color
MOVE A3 V1 ; P2 Color
SW T0 16(SP) ; P3 Color
SW T1 20(SP) ; P4 Color
JAL sprintf ; Creates String  
SW R0 24(SP) ; terminator byte

JAL GetPlayerCharacterString ; At V0, V1, T2, and T0
NOP 

SW R0 24(SP)
LI A0 -1 ; (No character image)
LUI A1 hi(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
MOVE A2 V0 ; P1 Name
MOVE A3 V1 ; P2 Name
SW T2 16(SP) ; P3 Name
JAL ShowMessage
SW T0 20(SP) ; P4 Name
 
; A0 is Window ID, returned by ShowMessage on A0
JAL DisableOptions_Dicey
NOP

;JAL AIChoice_Winter2
;NOP

LI A0 2
JAL GetBasicPromptSelection
MOVE A1 V0
MOVE S0 V0 ; S7 now has the chosen option index

JAL CloseMessage_Function
NOP

SLTI T0 S0 4 ; ON IF selected a Player
BNEZ T0 diceyjunctionscontinue
NOP
LI T0 4
BEQ S0 T0 movementspell
NOP
JAL ViewBoardMap
NOP
J diceyjunctions
NOP

diceyjunctionscontinue:
BNEZ FP diceyjunctionsproteanskip ; If not 0, Protean Ace was used, skip cost
NOP

LI T1 2
SUBU S1 S1 T1 ; Subtract 2 Pages
SB S1 0(S2) ; Store new number of Pages

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x1D1 ; Page Subtract Sound

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 30 ; Frames

diceyjunctionsproteanskip:
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 S0 ; Shift Left by Chosen Player Index 

LUI T3 hi(0x800CD09A)
ADDIU T3 T3 lo(0x800CD09A) ; Dicey Junctions Flag Address
LBU T4 0(T3) ; Flag Value

ADDU T4 T4 T2 ; Add to get new flag value
SB T4 0(T3) ; Store new flag

LI A0 0 ; Bar Code fade-out
JAL InitFadeOut
LI A1 16 ; 16 Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 16

LUI T0 hi(current_player_index)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(current_player_index)
SB S0 0(T0) ; Change active player

LI A0 0 ; Bar Code fade-in
JAL InitFadeIn
LI A1 16 ; 16 Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 16

JAL PlaySound 
LI A0 0xC2 ; Dizzy Sound Index

LUI A1 hi(DiceyJunctionsAlert_Message)
JAL ShowMessage_Function
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(DiceyJunctionsAlert_Message)

LI A0 0 ; Bar Code fade-out
JAL InitFadeOut
LI A1 16 ; 16 Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 16

LUI T0 hi(current_player_index)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(current_player_index)
LBU T1 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
SB T1 0(T0) ; Change active player back

LI A0 0 ; Bar Code fade-in
JAL InitFadeIn
LI A1 16 ; 16 Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 16

J flipitemuseflag
NOP

;=======================================================================================LOADED DICE

loadeddice:
SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
LI A0 -1 ; Character image (None)
LUI A1 hi(LoadedDice_Prompt)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(LoadedDice_Prompt)
LI A2 0
JAL ShowMessage
LI A3 0

;JAL GetRandomByte ; at V0
;NOP
;LI T0 5
;DIVU V0 T0

LI A0 2
JAL GetBasicPromptSelection
LW A1 76(SP)
MOVE S0 V0 ; S0 now has the chosen option index

; Obligatory message box closing/cleanup calls.
JAL 0x800EC6C8
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

; Change the outcome based on the choice.
SLTI T0 S0 5 ; ON IF player selected a dice roll number
BNEZ T0 addloadeddice 
NOP
LI A0 5
BEQ S0 A0 movementspell
NOP
JAL ViewBoardMap
NOP
J loadeddice
NOp

addloadeddice:
BNEZ FP addloadeddiceproteanskip
NOP

LI T1 4
SUBU S1 S1 T1 ; Subtract 4 Pages
SB S1 0(S2) ; Store new number of Pages

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x1D1 ; Page Subtract Sound

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 30 ; Frames

addloadeddiceproteanskip:
LUI T0 hi(0x800CDBD2)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(0x800CDBD2) ; P1 Forced Roll Address

LBU T4 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
LI T2 0x4C ; Distance between each player's addresses
MULT T4 T2 ; Multiply Current Player Index by T2
MFLO T2 ; Move Result to T2
ADDU T0 T0 T2 ; Add to get current Player's Forced Roll address

ADDIU S0 S0 1 ; Add 1 to chosen option index for dice roll
SB S0 0(T0) 

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x103 ; Dice Hit Sound Index

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 20

J flipitemuseflag
NOP

spellexplanations_movement:
LUI A1 hi(BroomZoomExplanation_Message)
JAL ShowMessage_Function
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(BroomZoomExplanation_Message)

LUI A1 hi(DiceyJunctionsExplanation_Message)
JAL ShowMessage_Function
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(DiceyJunctionsExplanation_Message)

LUI A1 hi(LoadedDiceExplanation_Message)
JAL ShowMessage_Function
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(LoadedDiceExplanation_Message)

J movementspell
NOP

;==============================
itemspell:
JAL GetColorFormatter_Item 
NOP ; returns color for 2nd and 3rd option on V0, V1, and T0-2 

LUI A0 hi(A_Pointer_with_enough_space) 
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(A_Pointer_with_enough_space) ; Parse Destination 
LUI A1 hi(Item_Prompt) 
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(Item_Prompt) ; String Format 
MOVE A2 V0 ; 1st Option Color 
MOVE A3 V1 ; 2nd Option Color 
SW T0 16(SP) ; 3rd Option Color 
JAL sprintf ; Creates String  
SW R0 20(SP) ; Terminator 

SW R0 16(SP) 
SW R0 20(SP) 
SW R0 24(SP) 
LI A0 -1 ; (None) 
LUI A1 hi(A_Pointer_with_enough_space) 
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(A_Pointer_with_enough_space) 
LI A2 0 
JAL ShowMessage 
LI A3 0 

JAL DisableOptions_3 ; A0 has Window ID 
NOP 

;JAL AIChoice_Autumn 
NOP 

LI A0 2 ; Pick whatever is in A1 as AI's Choice 
JAL GetBasicPromptSelection 
LI A1 2 ; Dual Wield
MOVE S0 V0 ; Chosen answer at S0 

JAL CloseMessage_Function 
NOP 

BEQZ S0 itemlock
NOP
LI T0 1
BEQ S0 T0 betterbarter
NOP
LI T0 2
BEQ S0 T0 dualwield
NOP
LI T0 3
BEQ S0 T0 spellexplanations_item
NOP
LI T0 4
BEQ S0 T0 firstprompt
NOP
JAL ViewBoardMap
NOP
J itemspell
NOP

;=====================================================================================BETTER BARTER

betterbarter:
BNEZ FP betterbarterproteanskip
NOP

LI T1 4
SUBU S1 S1 T1 ; Subtract 4 Pages
SB S1 0(S2) ; Store new number of Pages

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x1D1 ; Page Subtract Sound

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 30 ; Frames

betterbarterproteanskip:
LI S0 0 ; Start with Player 1
betterbarterplayerstruct:
JAL CheckMagicVeil ; 0 if not active, 1 if active
MOVE A0 S0 ; Player's Index

BNEZL V0 betterbarterplayerstruct
ADDIU S0 S0 1

LI S5 0 ; Start with first Item slot
LI S7 0 ; Start with first index of Array
LI T0 4 
BEQ S0 T0 flipitemuseflag ; exit once all players are checked
NOP
JAL GetPlayerStruct
MOVE A0 S0 
ADDIU S6 V0 24 ; Add to get first Item Slot address
betterbartermushroomloop:
LI T0 3
BEQL S5 T0 betterbarterplayerstruct ; check next player once all Item slots are checked
ADDIU S0 S0 1 ; add 1 to check next player IF branching
ADDU T5 S6 S5 ; Add to get current Item Slot in the loop
LBU S3 0(T5) ; Load Item Slot Value
LI T2 0xFF ; No item
BEQL S3 T2 betterbarterplayerstruct ; check next player if no item was found
ADDIU S0 S0 1 ; add 1 to check next player IF branching
LUI T0 hi(Mushroom_Array)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(Mushroom_Array)
ADDU T0 T0 S7
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Load Item Index Array Value
BEQ T1 T2 betterbarterotheritems ; check for other items if array is 0xFF
NOP
BEQ T1 S3 betterbartermushroomexchange
NOP
J betterbartermushroomloop
ADDIU S7 S7 1 ; Check next spot in the array

betterbarterotheritems:
LI T1 7 ; Bowser Phone index
BEQ S3 T1 betterbarterphone
NOP
LI T1 4 ; Cellular Shopper index
BEQ S3 T1 betterbartergiveitem
LI T0 7 ; give Bowser Phone
LI T1 6 ; Plunder Chest index
BEQ S3 T1 betterbartergiveitem
LI T0 0x10 ; give Barter Box
LI T1 9 ; Lucky Lamp index
BEQ S3 T1 betterbartergiveitem
LI T0 0xE ; give Magic Lamp
LI T1 0xB ; Boo Bell index
BEQ S3 T1 betterbartergiveitem
LI T0 0xC ; give Boo Repellant
LI T1 0xC ; Boo Repellant index
BEQ S3 T1 betterbartergiveitem
LI T0 0xB ; give Boo Bell
LI T1 0xD ; Bowser Suit index
BEQ S3 T1 betterbartergiveitem
LI T0 7 ; give Bowser Phone
LI T1 0xE ; Magic Lamp index
BEQ S3 T1 betterbartergiveitem
LI T0 9 ; give Lucky Lamp
LI T1 0x10 ; Barter Box index
BEQ S3 T1 betterbartergiveitem
LI T0 6 ; give Plunder Chest
; If we reach here, the player didn't have an affected item
ADDIU S5 S5 1 ; search the next Item slot
J betterbartermushroomloop
LI S7 0 ; Start with first index of Array again

betterbartergiveitem:
ADDU T5 S6 S5 ; Add to get current Item Slot in the loop
SB T0 0(T5) ; Store new Item

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 25 ; Got Item Sound Index

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 15 ; Frames

ADDIU S5 S5 1 ; search the next Item slot
J betterbartermushroomloop
LI S7 0 ; Start with first index of Array again

betterbarterphone:
JAL GetRandomByte ; 0 - 255 at V0
NOP
LI T0 2
DIVU V0 T0
MFHI T4
LUI T0 hi(Phone_Array)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(Phone_Array)
ADDU T0 T0 T4 ; Add to get item index in array
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Item Index
ADDU T5 S6 S5 ; Add to get current Item Slot in the loop
SB T1 0(T5) ; Give Item

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 25 ; Got Item Sound Index

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 15 ; Frames

ADDIU S5 S5 1 ; search the next Item slot
J betterbartermushroomloop
LI S7 0 ; Start with first index of Array again

;betterbarternextplayer:
;ADDIU S0 S0 1 ; Search next player
;J betterbarterplayerstruct
;LI S5 0 ; back to first item slot

betterbartermushroomexchange:
JAL GetRandomByte ; 0 - 255 at V0
NOP
LI T0 4
DIVU V0 T0
MFHI T4
LUI T0 hi(Mushroom_Array)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(Mushroom_Array)
ADDU T0 T0 T4 ; Add to get item index in array
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Item Index
BEQ T1 S3 betterbartermushroomexchange ; branch if it's the same item they had
NOP
ADDU T5 S6 S5 ; Add to get current Item Slot in the loop
SB T1 0(T5) ; Give Item

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 25 ; Got Item Sound Index

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 15 ; Frames

ADDIU S5 S5 1 ; search the next Item slot
J betterbartermushroomloop
LI S7 0 ; Start with first index of Array again

;=========================================================================================ITEM LOCK

itemlock:
JAL GetColorFormatter_ItemLock ; in T1, T3, T4, and T5 
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Pass Current Player's Index

LUI A0 hi(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(A_Pointer_with_enough_space) ; Parse Destination
LUI A1 hi(DiceyJunctions_Prompt)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(DiceyJunctions_Prompt) ; String Format
MOVE A2 V0 ; P1 Color
MOVE A3 V1 ; P2 Color
SW T0 16(SP) ; P3 Color
SW T1 20(SP) ; P4 Color
JAL sprintf ; Creates String  
SW R0 24(SP) ; terminator byte

JAL GetPlayerCharacterString ; At V0, V1, T2, and T0
NOP 

SW R0 24(SP)
LI A0 -1 ; (No character image)
LUI A1 hi(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
MOVE A2 V0 ; P1 Name
MOVE A3 V1 ; P2 Name
SW T2 16(SP) ; P3 Name
JAL ShowMessage
SW T0 20(SP) ; P4 Name
 
; A0 is Window ID, returned by ShowMessage on A0
JAL DisableOptions_Dicey
NOP

;JAL AIChoice_Winter2
;NOP

LI A0 2
JAL GetBasicPromptSelection
MOVE A1 V0
MOVE S0 V0 ; S7 now has the chosen option index

JAL CloseMessage_Function
NOP

SLTI T0 S0 4 ; ON IF selected a Player
BNEZ T0 itemlockcontinue
NOP
LI T0 4
BEQ S0 T0 itemspell
NOP
JAL ViewBoardMap
NOP
J itemlock
NOP

itemlockcontinue:
BNEZ FP itemlockcontinueproteanskip
NOP

LI T1 2
SUBU S1 S1 T1 ; Subtract 2 Pages
SB S1 0(S2) ; Store new number of Pages

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x1D1 ; Page Subtract Sound

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 30 ; Frames

itemlockcontinueproteanskip:
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 S0 ; Shift Left by Chosen Player Index 

LUI T3 hi(0x800CD09B)
ADDIU T3 T3 lo(0x800CD09B) ; Item Lock Flag Address
LBU T4 0(T3) ; Flag Value

ADDU T4 T4 T2 ; Add to get new flag value
SB T4 0(T3) ; Store new flag


LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
SLLV T2 T1 A0 ; Shift Left by Current Player Index 

AND V0 T4 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Curse is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ V0 itemlockcontinue2
NOP

LI T1 1
LBU T5 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
SLLV T2 T1 T5 ; Shift Left by Current Player Index

ADDU T4 T4 T2 ; Add to get new flag value
SB T4 0(T3) ; Store new flag

itemlockcontinue2:
LI A0 0 ; Bar Code fade-out
JAL InitFadeOut
LI A1 16 ; 16 Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 16

LUI T0 hi(current_player_index)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(current_player_index)
SB S0 0(T0) ; Change active player

LI A0 0 ; Bar Code fade-in
JAL InitFadeIn
LI A1 16 ; 16 Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 16

JAL PlaySound 
LI A0 0x1A7; Item Lock Sound Index

LUI A1 hi(ItemLockAlert_Message)
JAL ShowMessage_Function
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(ItemLockAlert_Message)

LI A0 0 ; Bar Code fade-out
JAL InitFadeOut
LI A1 16 ; 16 Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 16

LUI T0 hi(current_player_index)

NOP

SB S1 0(S2) ; Store new number of Pages

;AND V0 T4 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Curse is not active, 1 if it is.
;BNEZ V0 flipitemuseflag
;NOP

ADDU T4 T4 T2 ; Add to get new flag value
SB T4 0(T3) ; Store new flag

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x2DF ; Sparkly Sfx

; S0 = ModelSpaceData
; S7 = ModelDataFromPointer

; ==GET MODEL SPACE DATA==
LBU A0 15(S4) ; Chain Index
JAL GetAbsSpaceIndexFromChainSpaceIndex
LBU A1 16(S4) ; Chain Space Index

JAL GetSpaceData
MOVE A0 V0 ; True Space Index
MOVE S0 V0

; ==GET MODEL DATA FROM POINTER==
LI A0 56 ; 2 Tiny Stars pulsing
JAL 0x800D90C8
LI A1 0

MOVE S7 V0 ; Copy to S7

; ==PUT MODEL ON SPACE==
MOVE A1 S0
ADDIU A1 A1 8
MOVE A0 V0
ADDIU A0 A0 12 
JAL 0x80089A20 ; SetModelOnBoard
NOP

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 60 ; Frames

LUI A1 hi(MagicVeilActivation_Message)
JAL ShowMessage_Function
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(MagicVeilActivation_Message)

NOP

JAL GetRandomByte ; at V0
NOP
LI T0 4
DIVU V0 T0
MFHI S7 ; 0 - 3

LBU T2 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
BEQ S7 T2 bookbanditloop
NOP
JAL CheckMagicVeil
MOVE A0 S7 ; Player Index generated

BNEZ V0 bookbanditloop ; loop if player has Magic Veil active
NOP

LI T0 0x800CD096

LBU T4 0(T3) ; Chosen Player's Page Count
BEQZ T4 bookbanditloop ; loop if that player has no Pages
NOP

ADDIU T4 T4 -1 ; Subtract 1 Page
SB T4 0(T3) ; Store new number of Pages
ADDIU S1 S1 1 ; Add 1 to current player's Page count
SLTI T6 S1 11 ; ON IF 0-11
BEQL T6 R0 bookbanditstorepages
LI S1 10 ; Make it 10 Pages if more than 10

SB S1 0(S2) ; Store new number of Pages

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x1CF ; Ding Sound

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 30 ; Frames

ADDIU S0 S0 -1 ; Subtract 1 from loop count
BEQZ S0 flipitemuseflag ; exit once all Pages have been taken
NOP 
J bookbanditloop ; ELSE take from a player again
NOP

.align 16
GetChainAndSpaceIndexFromAbsSpaceIndex:
//takes arg a0, abs_space_index
//returns chain_index to v0
//returns space_index to v1
ADDIU sp, sp, -0x40 
SW ra, 0x0018 (sp)
SW s0, 0x001C (sp)
SW s1, 0x0020 (sp)
SW s2, 0x0024 (sp)
SW s3, 0x0028 (sp)
SW s4, 0x002C (sp)
SW s5, 0x0030 (sp)
SW s6, 0x0034 (sp)
ORI s3, r0, 0x0000 //init s3 to 0
ADDIU s4, r0, 0xFFFF //init s4 to FFFF, loop1 counter
LUI s0, 0x8010
LW s0, 0x5218 (s0) //load ptr to beginning of hydrated chains ptr
DADDU s1, a0, r0 ;move abs_space_index to s0
Loop:
ADDIU s4, s4, 0x0001 //add 1 to current loop total
LHU s2, 0x0000 (s0) //load total number of space_indicies in chain
BEQ s2, r0, error
NOP
ORI t0, r0, 0x0000 //going to be used for loop 2 counter
LW s3, 0x0004 (s0) //load pointer that points to abs space_indicies for current chain in loop
Loop2:
//
LHU t1, 0x0000 (s3) //load abs value from hydrated chain
BEQ t1, s1, isabs
NOP
ADDIU t0, t0, 0x0001 //add 1 to loop2 counter
BEQ t0, s2, backtoLoop1
NOP
BEQ r0, r0, Loop2
ADDIU s3, s3, 0x0002
returnvalues:
//
GetChainAndSpaceIndexFromAbsSpaceIndex_exit:
LW ra, 0x0018 (sp)
LW s0, 0x001C (sp)
LW s1, 0x0020 (sp)
LW s2, 0x0024 (sp)
LW s3, 0x0028 (sp)
LW s4, 0x002C (sp)
LW s5, 0x0030 (sp)
LW s6, 0x0034 (sp)
JR RA
ADDIU sp, sp, 0x40
error:
ORI v0, r0, 0xFFFF //error, return FFFF
BEQ r0, r0, GetChainAndSpaceIndexFromAbsSpaceIndex_exit
ORI v1, r0, 0xFFFF //error, return FFFF
isabs:
//s4 holds current chain index
//t1 holds current space index in chain
ADD v0, s4, r0 //move chain index to v0
BEQ r0, r0, GetChainAndSpaceIndexFromAbsSpaceIndex_exit
ADD v1, t0, r0 //move space_index to v1
backtoLoop1:
BEQ r0, r0, Loop
ADDIU s0, s0, 0x0008 //advance to next hydrated chains ptr

NOP

NOP 

betterbarterproteanski:
LI T5 4 ; Counter to shut down Better Barter
LI T2 0x800D1120 ; P1 Item 1
LBU T6 0(T2) ; P1 Item Value
LI T3 0xFF ; No Item Value
BEQL T6 T3 checkforbetterbarter2

checkforbetterbarter2:

LBU T6 0(T2) ; P2 Item Value
LI T3 0xFF ; No Item Value
BEQL T6 T3 checkforbetterbarter3
ADDIU T5 T5 -1 ; Subtract 1 if P1 has no item
checkforbetterbarter3:
LI T2 0x800D1190 ; P3 Item 1
LBU T6 0(T2) ; P3 Item Value
LI T3 0xFF ; No Item Value
BEQL T6 T3 checkforbetterbarter4
ADDIU T5 T5 -1 ; Subtract 1 if P1 has no item
checkforbetterbarter4:
LI T2 0x800D11C8 ; P4 Item 1
LBU T6 0(T2) ; P4 Item Value
LI T3 0xFF ; No Item Value
BEQL T6 T3 checkforbetterbarter5
ADDIU T5 T5 -1 ; Subtract 1 if P1 has no item
checkforbetterbarter5:
BEQZ T5 checkfordualwield ; If 0, no one has items, disable Better Barter
NOP

LUI V1 hi(RedColor_ptr) ; Red Color

NOP

NOP 

checkfordualwieldproteanskip:
LBU T6 24(S4) ; Item Slot #1
LI T2 0xFF ; No Item

BEQ T6 T2 GetColorFormatter_Item_exit ; exit if there's no item in slot #1
NOP

LBU T6 26(S4) ; Item Slot #3
LI T2 0xFF ; No Item

BNE T6 T2 GetColorFormatter_Item_exit ; exit if there's an item in slot #3
NOP

LUI T0 hi(RedColor_ptr) 
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(RedColor_ptr) ; Third Option (Item Spell) 
SB T8 2(T7) ; Don't disable 3rd Option

GetColorFormatter_ItemLock:
ADDIU SP SP -60
SW RA 56(SP)

LUI V0 hi(BlackColor_ptr)
ADDIU V0 V0 lo(BlackColor_ptr) ; First Option (First Player)
LUI V1 hi(BlackColor_ptr)
ADDIU V1 V1 lo(BlackColor_ptr) ; Second Option (Second Player)
LUI T0 hi(BlackColor_ptr)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(BlackColor_ptr) ; Third Option (Third Player)
LUI T1 hi(BlackColor_ptr)
ADDIU T1 T1 lo(BlackColor_ptr) ; Fourth Option (Fourth Player)
LUI T7 hi(OptionsToDisable_Dicey)
ADDIU T7 T7 lo(OptionsToDisable_Dicey) ; Array of answers to disable

LBU T4 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
LI T5 0 ; Player 1 Index
BEQ T4 T5 checkplayer2_ItemLock
NOP
LI T3 1 
SLL T2 T3 0 ; Shift Left by Player 1 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer2_ItemLock
NOP
LI A1 0x800CD09B ; Item Lock Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer2_ItemLock
NOP

LUI V0 hi(WhiteColor_ptr) ; White Color   
ADDIU V0 V0 lo(WhiteColor_ptr)   
LI T8 6 ; No option to Disable   
SB T8 0(T7) ; Don't disable 1st Player

checkplayer2_ItemLock:
LBU T4 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
LI T5 1 ; Player 2 Index
BEQ T4 T5 checkplayer3_ItemLock
NOP
LI T3 1 
SLL T2 T3 1 ; Shift Left by Player 2 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer3_ItemLock
NOP
LI A1 0x800CD09B ; Item Lock Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer3_ItemLock
NOP

LUI V1 hi(WhiteColor_ptr) ; White Color   
ADDIU V1 V1 lo(WhiteColor_ptr)   
LI T8 6 ; No option to Disable   
SB T8 1(T7) ; Don't disable 2nd Player

checkplayer3_ItemLock:
LBU T4 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
LI T5 2 ; Player 3 Index
BEQ T4 T5 checkplayer4_ItemLock
NOP
LI T3 1 
SLL T2 T3 2 ; Shift Left by Player 3 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer4_ItemLock
NOP
LI A1 0x800CD09B ; Item Lock Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer4_ItemLock
NOP

LUI T0 hi(WhiteColor_ptr) ; White Color   
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(WhiteColor_ptr)   
LI T8 6 ; No option to Disable   
SB T8 2(T7) ; Don't disable 3rd Player

checkplayer4_ItemLock:
LBU T4 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
LI T5 3 ; Player 4 Index
BEQ T4 T5 GetColorFormatter_ItemLock_exit
NOP
LI T3 1 
SLL T2 T3 3 ; Shift Left by Player 4 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 GetColorFormatter_ItemLock_exit
NOP
LI A1 0x800CD09B ; Item Lock Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 GetColorFormatter_ItemLock_exit
NOP

LUI T1 hi(WhiteColor_ptr) ; White Color   
ADDIU T1 T1 lo(WhiteColor_ptr)   
LI T8 6 ; No option to Disable   
SB T8 3(T7) ; Don't disable 3rd Player

GetColorFormatter_Coin:

ADDIU V1 V1 lo(BlackColor_ptr) ; Second Option (Crystal Coin)  
LUI T0 hi(BlackColor_ptr)

LUI T7 hi(OptionsToDisable_3)

LI T6 0x800CD09F ; Zap Wire Space Index Address
LBU T6 0(T6)
BNEZ T6 CheckforCrystalCoin
NOP

LUI V0 hi(YellowColor_ptr) ; Yellow Color

NOP

GetColorFormatter_Magic:   
ADDIU SP SP -60   
SW RA 56(SP)   

LUI V0 hi(PurpleColor_ptr)   
ADDIU V0 V0 lo(PurpleColor_ptr) ; First Option (Magic Veil)   
LUI V1 hi(BlackColor_ptr)   
ADDIU V1 V1 lo(BlackColor_ptr) ; Second Option (Protean Ace)   
LUI T0 hi(BlackColor_ptr)   
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(BlackColor_ptr) ; Third Option (Book Bandit)   
LUI T7 hi(OptionsToDisable_3)   
ADDIU T7 T7 lo(OptionsToDisable_3) ; Array of answers to disable  

LI T8 6 ; No option to Disable
SB T8 0(T7) ; Don't disable 1st Option (Magic Veil)

BNEZ FP bookbanditproteanaceski
NOP
SLTI T6 S1 4 ; ON IF not enough Pages for Book Bandit   
BNEZ T6 checkproteanace ; exit Protean Ace if not enough 
NOP

bookbanditproteanaceski:
LI T4 0x800CD096
LI T5 0 ; Start Page Count at 0
LBU T3 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
BEQZ T3 checkplayer2
NOP

LI T1 1 
SLL T2 T1 0 ; Shift Left by Player 1 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer2
NOP

LBU T5 0(T4) ; Player 1's Page Count
checkplayer2:
LI T4 0x800CD097 ; Check Player 2's Pages
LI T6 1
BEQ T3 T6 checkplayer3
NOP

LI T1 1 
SLL T2 T1 1 ; Shift Left by Player 2 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer3
NOP

LBU T9 0(T4) ; Player 2's Page Value
ADDU T5 T5 T9 ; Add Total
checkplayer3:
LI T4 0x800CD098 ; Check Player 3's Pages
LI T6 2
BEQ T3 T6 checkplayer4
NOP

LI T1 1 
SLL T2 T1 2 ; Shift Left by Player 3 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer4
NOP

LBU T9 0(T4) ; Player 3's Page Value
ADDU T5 T5 T9 ; Add Total
checkplayer4:
LI T4 0x800CD099 ; Check Player 4's Pages
LI T6 3
BEQ T3 T6 checkfor5pagestotal
NOP

LI T1 1 
SLL T2 T1 3 ; Shift Left by Player 4 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkfor5pagestotal
NOP

LBU T9 0(T4) ; Player 4's Page Value
ADDU T5 T5 T9 ; Add Total

checkfor5pagestotal:
SLTI T2 T5 3 ; ON IF 0 - 2
BNEZ T2 checkproteanace
NOP

LUI T0 hi(PurpleColor_ptr) ; Purple Color   
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(PurpleColor_ptr)   
LI T8 6 ; No option to Disable   
SB T8 2(T7) ; Don't disable 3rd Option (Book Bandit)   

checkproteanace:
BNEZ FP GetColorFormatter_Magic_exit
NOP
SLTI T6 S1 3 ; ON IF not enough Pages for Protean Ace   
BNEZ T6 GetColorFormatter_Magic_exit ; exit if not enough Pages    
NOP   

LBU T2 24(S4) ; First Item Slot
LI T3 0xFF ; No Item
BEQ T2 T3 GetColorFormatter_Magic_exit ; exit if they don't have an item
NOP

LI T2 0x800CD0A9 ; Can use Item Flag Address
LBU T3 0(T2) ; Can use Item Flag Value
BNEZ T3 GetColorFormatter_Magic_exit ; exit if they can't use an item
NOP

LUI V1 hi(PurpleColor_ptr)   
ADDIU V1 V1 lo(PurpleColor_ptr) ; Third Option (Protean Ace)   
SB T8 1(T7) ; Don't disable 2nd Option   

GetColorFormatter_Magic_exit:   
LW RA 56(SP)   
JR RA    
ADDIU SP SP 60

GetTurnAndPlacing:
ADDIU SP SP -64
SW RA 60(SP)

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex ; At V0
NOP

JAL GetPlayerPlacementAtEndOfGame ; 0-3 at V0
MOVE A0 V0

LUI T1 hi(current_turn)
ADDIU T1 T1 lo(current_turn) ; Loading address of current turn number
LBU T1 0(T1) ; Loading current turn number
LUI T0 hi(total_turns)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(total_turns) ; Loading address of total turn number
LBU T0 0(T0) ; Loading total turn number

SLTI T3 T1 6 ; ON IF current turn is less than 6
BNE T3 R0 addplacing ; If it's less than 6, then it's Early Game, exit
LI T7 0 ; Early Game Value on T7

SUB T2 T0 T1
SLTI T3 T2 5 ; ON IF Total Turns - Current Turn = 4 or less
BNE T3 R0 addplacing ; If it's 4 or less, it's Lategame, exit
LI T7 8 ; Late Game Value on T7

LI T7 4 ; Mid Game Value on T7

addplacing:
MOVE V1 T7 ; V1 now contains Turn Tier
ADDU V0 T7 V0 ; Placing + Turn Tier at V0

LW RA 60(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 64

.align 16

ADDIU SP SP -56
SW RA 52(SP)

JAL GetPlayerStruct ; at V0
LI A0 -1

LBU T0 2(V0)

MULT T2 T0 ;  Multiply Controller value by 2
MFLO T0 ; Move the result to S3

ADDU T1 T1 T0 ; Add result to get Current Player's Input Address
LBU V1 0(T1) ; Load address value into V0

LI T2 8
BEQ T2 V1 DetectCStickInputexit
LI V0 1 ; exits with 1 if up
LI T2 1
BEQ T2 V1 DetectCStickInputexit
LI V0 1 ; exits with 1 if right
LI T2 4
BEQ T2 V1 DetectCStickInputexit
LI V0 -1 ; exits with -1 if down
LI T2 2
BEQ T2 V1 DetectCStickInputexit
LI V0 -1 ; exits with -1 if left
LI V0 0 ; ELSE 0

JR RA

GetAIChoice:
ADDIU SP SP -80
SW RA 76(SP)


SLTI T0 S1 4 ; ON IF 0-3 Pages
BNEZ T0 AICheckDualWield
NOP

JAL GetPlayerPlacementAtEndOfGame
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player Index

SLTI T0 V0 2 ; ON IF 0-1
BNEZ T0 AICheckDualWield
NOP

LBU A0 15(S4) ; Current Chain Index
JAL GetAbsSpaceIndexFromChainSpaceIndex
LBU A1 16(S4) ; Current Chain Space Index

LI T0 67
BEQ V0 T0 AILoadedDice1 ; 
NOP
LI T0 66
BEQ V0 T0 AILoadedDice2 ; 
NOP
LI T0 65
BEQ V0 T0 AILoadedDice3 ; 
NOP
LI T0 64
BEQ V0 T0 AILoadedDice4 ; 
NOP
LI T0 61
BEQ V0 T0 AILoadedDice5 ; 
NOP

J AICheckDualWield
NOP

AILoadedDice1:
LI V0 0 ; Movement Spell Choice
J GetAIChoice_exit
LI V1 0 ; Select 1 as the number to roll

AILoadedDice2:
LI V0 0 ; Movement Spell Choice
J GetAIChoice_exit
LI V1 1 ; Select 2 as the number to roll

AILoadedDice3:
LI V0 0 ; Movement Spell Choice
J GetAIChoice_exit
LI V1 2 ; Select 3 as the number to roll

AILoadedDice4:
LI V0 0 ; Movement Spell Choice
J GetAIChoice_exit
LI V1 3 ; Select 4 as the number to roll

AILoadedDice5:
LI V0 0 ; Movement Spell Choice
J GetAIChoice_exit
LI V1 4 ; Select 5 as the number to roll

AICheckDualWield:
SLTI T0 S1 4 ; ON IF 0-3 Pages
BNEZ T0 AICheckBookBandit
NOP

JAL PlayerHasEmptyItemSlot ; at V0
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current player's Index
LI T0 -1 ; No item slot found
BEQ V0 T0 AICheckBookBandit ; Branch if full on items
NOP

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current player's Index
JAL PlayerHasItem ; 0, 1, 2, or -1 at V0
LI A1 0xE ; Magic Lamp

LI T0 -1 ; Item Not Found index
BNE V0 T0 AICheckDualWield2
NOP

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current player's Index
JAL PlayerHasItem ; 0, 1, 2, or -1 at V0
LI A1 6 ; Plunder Chest

LI T0 -1 ; Item Not Found index
BNE V0 T0 AICheckDualWield2
NOP

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current player's Index
JAL PlayerHasItem ; 0, 1, 2, or -1 at V0
LI A1 10 ; Golden Mushroom

LI T0 -1 ; Item Not Found index
BNE V0 T0 AICheckDualWield2
NOP

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current player's Index
JAL PlayerHasItem ; 0, 1, 2, or -1 at V0
LI A1 11 ; Boo Bell

LI T0 -1 ; Item Not Found index
BNE V0 T0 AICheckDualWield2
NOP

J AICheckBookBandit
NOP

AICheckDualWield2:
MOVE V1 V0 ; Item Index in array
J GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 1 ; Item Spell Choice


AICheckBookBandit:
SLTI T0 S1 4 ; ON IF 0-3 Pages
BNEZ T0 AICheckCrystalCoin
NOP

LI T4 0x800CD096
LI T5 0 ; Start Page Count at 0
LBU T3 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
BEQZ T3 checkplayer2_2
NOP

LI T1 1 
SLL T2 T1 0 ; Shift Left by Player 1 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer2_2
NOP

LBU T5 0(T4) ; Player 1's Page Count
checkplayer2_2:
LI T4 0x800CD097 ; Check Player 2's Pages
LI T6 1
BEQ T3 T6 checkplayer3_2
NOP

LI T1 1 
SLL T2 T1 1 ; Shift Left by Player 2 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer3_2
NOP

LBU T9 0(T4) ; Player 2's Page Value
ADDU T5 T5 T9 ; Add Total
checkplayer3_2:
LI T4 0x800CD098 ; Check Player 3's Pages
LI T6 2
BEQ T3 T6 checkplayer4_2
NOP

LI T1 1 
SLL T2 T1 2 ; Shift Left by Player 3 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer4_2
NOP

LBU T9 0(T4) ; Player 3's Page Value
ADDU T5 T5 T9 ; Add Total
checkplayer4_2:
LI T4 0x800CD099 ; Check Player 4's Pages
LI T6 3
BEQ T3 T6 checkfor5pagestotal_2
NOP

LI T1 1 
SLL T2 T1 3 ; Shift Left by Player 4 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkfor5pagestotal_2
NOP

LBU T9 0(T4) ; Player 4's Page Value
ADDU T5 T5 T9 ; Add Total

checkfor5pagestotal_2:
SLTI T2 T5 7 ; ON IF 0 - 6
BNEZ T2 AICheckCrystalCoin
NOP
J GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 3 ; Magic Spell Choice


AICheckCrystalCoin:
SLTI T0 S1 3 ; ON IF 0-2 Pages
BNEZ T0 AICheckMetronome
NOP

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
JAL PlayerHasCoins ; 1 IF 5 or more
LI A1 5 ; Coins

BNEZ V0 AICheckMetronome
NOP

J GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 2 ; Coin Spell Choice

AICheckMetronome:
SLTI T2 T5 2 ; ON IF 0 - 1
BNEZL T2 GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 5 ; Choose Nothing Index

LUI T0 hi(current_turn)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(current_turn)
LBU T1 0(T0) 

SLTI T2 T1 11 ; ON if 1-10
BNEZL T2 GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 5 ; Chooce Nothing Index

JAL GetPlayerPlacementAtEndOfGame
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player Index

SLTI T0 V0 2 ; ON IF 0-1
BNEZL T2 GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 5 ; Chooce Nothing Index

JAL RNGPercentChance ; 25% of 1 at V0
LI A0 25 ; % chance

BNEZL V0 GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 4 ; Misc Spell Choice

LI V0 5 ; Choose Nothing Index

GetAIChoice_exit:
LW RA 76(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80

.align 16
cameramain:
ADDIU sp, sp, -0x30
SW ra, 0x0020 (sp)
SW s0, 0x0024 (sp)

;LI a0, test1
JAL setCameraPosToSpace
NOP

LW ra, 0x0020 (sp)
LW s0, 0x0024 (sp)
JR RA
ADDIU sp, sp, 0x30

getSpaceVec3f:
ADDIU sp, sp, -0x20
SW ra, 0x0018 (sp)
JAL GetSpaceData
NOP
ADDIU v0, v0, 8 //now points to XYZ of space
LW ra, 0x0018 (sp)
JR RA
ADDIU sp, sp, 0x20

setCameraCoords: //takes 1 arg0, Vec3f*
LI t0, 0x801049F0
LW t1, 0x0000 (a0) //load X
SW t1, 0x0000 (t0) //store X
LW t1, 0x0004 (a0) //load Y
JR RA
SW t1, 0x0004 (t0) //store Z

setCameraPosToSpace: //takes arg a0, space id
ADDIU sp, sp, -0x28
SW ra, 0x0020 (sp)

JAL getSpaceVec3f
NOP

DADDU a0, r0, r0
LI a2, tempVec2f
JAL 0x8001291C //Convert3DTo2D
ADDU a1, v0, r0

LI a0, tempVec2f
LI a1, posOffset
LWC1 f0, 0x0000 (a0)
LWC1 f2, 0x0000 (a1)
ADD.S f0, f0, f2
SWC1 f0, 0x0000 (a0)
LWC1 f0, 0x0004 (a0)
LWC1 f2, 0x0004 (a1)
ADD.S f0, f0, f2
SWC1 f0, 0x0004 (a0)
JAL setCameraCoords
NOP

LW ra, 0x0020 (sp)
JR RA
ADDIU sp, sp, 0x28


tempVec2f:
.word 0, 0

posOffset:
.float 10.0, 4.0

; NAME: [GG] Magic Intro

; PARAM: Space|ToP

NOP

NOP

.align 16
cameramain:
ADDIU sp, sp, -0x30
SW ra, 0x0020 (sp)
SW s0, 0x0024 (sp)

;LI a0, test1
JAL setCameraPosToSpace
NOP

LW ra, 0x0020 (sp)
LW s0, 0x0024 (sp)
JR RA
ADDIU sp, sp, 0x30

getSpaceVec3f:
ADDIU sp, sp, -0x20
SW ra, 0x0018 (sp)
JAL GetSpaceData
NOP
ADDIU v0, v0, 8 //now points to XYZ of space
LW ra, 0x0018 (sp)
JR RA
ADDIU sp, sp, 0x20

setCameraCoords: //takes 1 arg0, Vec3f*
LI t0, 0x801049F0
LW t1, 0x0000 (a0) //load X
SW t1, 0x0000 (t0) //store X
LW t1, 0x0004 (a0) //load Y
JR RA
SW t1, 0x0004 (t0) //store Z

setCameraPosToSpace: //takes arg a0, space id
ADDIU sp, sp, -0x28
SW ra, 0x0020 (sp)

JAL getSpaceVec3f
NOP

DADDU a0, r0, r0
LI a2, tempVec2f
JAL 0x8001291C //Convert3DTo2D
ADDU a1, v0, r0

LI a0, tempVec2f
LI a1, posOffset
LWC1 f0, 0x0000 (a0)
LWC1 f2, 0x0000 (a1)
ADD.S f0, f0, f2
SWC1 f0, 0x0000 (a0)
LWC1 f0, 0x0004 (a0)
LWC1 f2, 0x0004 (a1)
ADD.S f0, f0, f2
SWC1 f0, 0x0004 (a0)
JAL setCameraCoords
NOP

LW ra, 0x0020 (sp)
JR RA
ADDIU sp, sp, 0x28


tempVec2f:
.word 0, 0

posOffset:
.float 10.0, 4.0

BNE S1 T2 continue

SW R0 20(SP) ; A5

NOP

NOP

NOP

NOP

continue:

NOP

NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

SLTI T2 S1 8 ; ON IF 0-7 Pages
BEQZ T2 givepages

ADDIU S1 S1 2 ; Add 2 Pages
SLTI T0 S1 11 ; ON IF 2-10 Pages
BEQL T0 R0 give2pages

JAL PlaySound
ADDIU A0 T0 0x275 ; Mario's Happy Voice Index

LI A0 40 ; Frames

LI A1 -1 ; Idle Animation Index

LI A2 2 ; Loop animation

JAL PlaySound

LI A1 8 ; Frames it takes to turn

LI A1 8 ; Frames it takes to turn

pageprompt:

GetAIChoice:

NOP

NOP

ChooseNo:

loadchoicearray:

[GG] Library.code:
; NAME: [GG] Library
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: +Number|MaxDrinkAmount
; PARAM: +Number|DrinkPrice
; PARAM: Space|SpaceToFace

ADDIU SP SP -120
SW RA 116(SP)
SW S0 112(SP) ; Flag for exit ; Drink Count to Purchase Display
SW S1 108(SP) ; Drink Shop Inventory Count Address
SW S2 104(SP) ; Drink Shop Inventory Value
SW S7 100(SP) ; Message to Load
SW S4 96(SP) ; Current Player's Index
SW S5 92(SP) ; Drink Cost to Display
SW S3 88(SP) ; Current Player's Drink Count Value
SW S6 84(SP) ; Current Player's Drink Count Address
SW FP 80(SP) ; Max Amount of Drinks player can purchase



START:
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 -1 ; Idle Animation
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A2 2 ; Loop

LI A0 -1 ; Current Player's Index
LI A1 8 ; Frames it takes to turn
LI A2 SpaceToFace
JAL 0x800ED20C ; RotatePlayerModel
NOP

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 8

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex
NOP
MOVE S4 V0

LUI S6 hi(0x800CD096)
ADDIU S6 S6 lo(0x800CD096)
ADDU S6 S6 S4 ; S6 now holds current player's page count address
LBU S3 0(S6) ; S3 now holds current player's page count value

LI T0 MaxDrinkAmount
BEQ T0 S3 TooManyDrinks
NOP

MOVE A0 S4
JAL PlayerHasCoins
LI A1 DrinkPrice

BEQ V0 R0 NotEnoughCoins
NOP

LUI T0 hi(total_turns)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(total_turns)
LB T1 0(T0) 
LUI T0 hi(current_turn)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(current_turn)
LB T2 0(T0) 

BEQ T1 T2 LastTurn ; don't run if it's the last turn
NOP

LI S2 5 ; "Inventory"

LUI A0 hi(TotalDrinkCount_String)
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(TotalDrinkCount_String) ; Parse Destination
LUI A1 hi(percent_d)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(percent_d) ; String Format
MOVE A2 S2 ; Value to convert
JAL sprintf
LI A3 0

LUI A1 hi(Greeting_Message)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(Greeting_Message)
J DisplayMessage
LI S7 0 ; no exit

TooManyDrinks:
LUI A1 hi(TooManyDrinks_Message)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(TooManyDrinks_Message)
J DisplayMessage
LI S7 1 ; exit after message

NotEnoughCoins:
LUI A1 hi(NotEnoughCoins_Message)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(NotEnoughCoins_Message)
J DisplayMessage
LI S7 1 ; exit after message

LastTurn:
LUI A1 hi(LastTurn_Message)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(LastTurn_Message)
J DisplayMessage
LI S7 1 ; exit after message

DisplayMessage:
SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
LI A0 0x3C ; Character image (Jeanie)
LUI A2 hi(TotalDrinkCount_String)
ADDIU A2 A2 lo(TotalDrinkCount_String)
JAL ShowMessage
LI A3 0

JAL AIChoice ; AI's Choice at V0
NOP

LI A0 2
JAL GetBasicPromptSelection
MOVE A1 V0 ; A1 now has the AI's decision
MOVE S0 V0 ; S0 now has the receiver index

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL CloseMessage
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

BNE S7 R0 exit
NOP

BEQ S0 R0 yes
NOP
LI T0 1
BEQ S0 T0 no
NOP

JAL ViewBoardMap
NOP
J START
NOP

yes:
LI S5 DrinkPrice ; Cost for Drinks Display
LI S0 1 ; Drinks to Purchase Display

LI T0 MaxDrinkAmount
LI T9 1 ; Subtract 1 from Max amount to see
SUBU T0 T0 T9
BEQ S3 T0 PrintStrings
LI FP 1 ; Player can only buy 1 Drink

LI T4 MaxDrinkAmount
SUBU FP T4 S3 ; FP = Amount of drinks player needs to max
ADDIU T6 S2 1 ; T6 = Shop Inventory + 1 for SLT below
maxdrinkinventoryloop:
SLT T5 FP T6 ; T5 = 1 if the Shop has the amount needed
BEQ T5 R0 shoplacksinventory
NOP ; ELSE means Shop has the needed drinks to max 
maxdrinkcoinloop:
MULT FP S5 ; multiply drink amount by price, result on lo
MFLO T7 ; move result to T7

MOVE A0 S4
JAL PlayerHasCoins ; 1 IF player can afford max drinks?
MOVE A1 T7

BEQ V0 R0 nocoins
NOP ; ELSE means they can afford max drinks

J PrintStrings
NOP

nocoins:
J maxdrinkcoinloop
ADDIU FP FP -1

shoplacksinventory:
J maxdrinkinventoryloop
ADDIU FP FP -1

PrintStrings:
LUI A0 hi(DrinkCountSelection_String)
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(DrinkCountSelection_String) ; Parse Destination
LUI A1 hi(percent_d)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(percent_d) ; String Format
MOVE A2 S0 ; Value to convert
JAL sprintf
LI A3 0

LUI A0 hi(Cost_String)
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(Cost_String) ; Parse Destination
LUI A1 hi(percent_d)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(percent_d) ; String Format
MOVE A2 S5 ; Value to convert
JAL sprintf
LI A3 0 

LUI A1 hi(DrinkSelection_Window)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(DrinkSelection_Window)
J DisplayMessage2
NOP

no:
LUI A1 hi(Goodbye_Message)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(Goodbye_Message)
LI S7 7 ; exit after message

DisplayMessage2:
LUI T1 hi(Cost_String)
ADDIU T1 T1 lo(Cost_String) 
SW T1 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
LI A0 0x3C ; Character image (Jeanie)
LI A2 0
LUI A3 hi(DrinkCountSelection_String)
ADDIU A3 A3 lo(DrinkCountSelection_String) 
JAL 0x800EC92C  ; ShowMessage2
NOP
SW A0 76(SP)

LI T2 7
BEQ S7 T2 exitclose
NOP

JAL PlayerIsCPU ; Returns 1 if the current player is a CPU
MOVE A0 S4

BNE V0 R0 checkcpudrinks
NOP

LoopReturn:
JAL DetectCStickInput ; V0 = 1 if Stick is Up, -1 if Down, ELSE 0
NOP

BEQ V0 R0 Loop
NOP

LI T0 1
BEQ V0 T0 CheckMax
NOP
J CheckMin
NOP

; S0 = Drink Count to Purchase (USED)
; S1 = Shop Inventory Address
; S2 = Shop Inventory Value
; S3 = Player's Drink Count Value
; S4 = Current Player's Index
; S5 = Coin Amount to Pay (USED) 
; S6 = Current Player's Drink Count Address
; S7 = Current Player's Coin Amount
; FP = Max Amount of Drinks the player can purchase

CheckMax:
BNE S0 FP ContinueNormal
NOP
LI S0 1 ; Make the display 1 Drink
LI S5 DrinkPrice ; Make the display base price
J ContinueRefresh
NOP

CheckMin:
LI T3 1 ; If the Display is 1 Drink when they press Down...
BNE S0 T3 ContinueNormal
NOP
MOVE S0 FP
LI T4 DrinkPrice
MULT T4 FP
MFLO S5
J ContinueRefresh
NOP

ContinueNormal:
ADDU S0 S0 V0
LI T0 DrinkPrice
MULT T0 S0
MFLO S5

ContinueRefresh:
LUI A0 hi(DrinkCountSelection_String)
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(DrinkCountSelection_String)
LUI A1 hi(percent_d)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(percent_d)
JAL sprintf
MOVE A2 S0

LUI A0 hi(Cost_String)
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(Cost_String)
LUI A1 hi(percent_d)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(percent_d)
JAL sprintf
MOVE A2 S5 

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 582 ; Coin Sound

JAL SleepVProcess
NOP

Loop:
JAL DetectABInput ; V0 = 1 if A press, 2 if B press, ELSE 0
NOP

LI T0 1
BEQ V0 T0 exitloop
NOP
BEQ V0 R0 ContinueInLoop
NOP

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 4 ; Back Sound Index

JAL 0x800EC6C8
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP
MOVE S2 S6
J START
NOP

ContinueInLoop:
LW A0 76(SP)
LUI A1 hi(DrinkCountSelection_String)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(DrinkCountSelection_String)
JAL 0x8005B6BC ; Updates Parameter?
MOVE A2 R0

LW A0 76(SP)
LUI A1 hi(Cost_String)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(Cost_String)
JAL 0x8005B6BC ; Updates Parameter?
MOVE A2 R0

LW A0 76(SP)
LUI A1 hi(DrinkSelection_Window)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(DrinkSelection_Window)
LI A2 -1
JAL 0x8005B43C ; Updates Message Window?
LI A3 -1

JAL SleepVProcess
NOP

J LoopReturn
NOP

checkcpudrinks:
MOVE S0 FP ; max amount purchaseable 
LI T0 DrinkPrice
MULTU T0 FP
MFLO S5 ; Price for Drinks

exitloop:
JAL 0x800EC6C8
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 583 ; Cash Register Sound

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 10 ; Sleep 10 frames


continuedrinkshop:
MOVE A0 S4
JAL AdjustPlayerCoinsGradual
SUBU A1 R0 S5

MOVE A0 S4
JAL ShowPlayerCoinChange
SUBU A1 R0 S5

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 30 ; Sleep 30 frames

SUBU S2 S2 S0 ; S2 loses the purchased drinks
ADDU S3 S3 S0 ; S3 gains the purchased drinks

LUI A0 hi(AfterPurchaseDrinkCount_String)
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(AfterPurchaseDrinkCount_String) ; Parse Destination
LUI A1 hi(percent_d)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(percent_d) ; String Format
MOVE A2 S2 ; Value to convert
JAL sprintf
LI A3 0

LUI T0 hi(AfterPurchaseDrinkCount_String)

;
JAL GetPlayerNamePtr

MainsPrintf:
ADDIU sp, sp, -0x60
SW ra, 0x0030 (sp)
SW a0, 0x0034 (sp)
SW a1, 0x0038 (sp)
SW a2, 0x003C (sp)
SW a3, 0x0040 (sp)
SW S0, 0x002C (SP)
SW S4, 0x0028 (SP)
SW S1, 0x0024 (SP)
;
LW a2, 0x0070 (sp) ;load character 1 ptr from stack
LW a3, 0x0074 (sp) ;load character 1 drink amount ptr from stack
LW a0, 0x0078 (sp) ;load character 2 pointer from stack
SW a0, 0x0010 (sp) ;store character 2 pointer to stack
;
LW a0, 0x007C (sp) ;load character 2 drink amount ptr from stack
SW a0, 0x0014 (sp) ;store character 2 drink amount ptr to stack
;
LW a0, 0x0080 (sp) ;load character 3 pointer from stack
SW a0, 0x0018 (sp) ;store character 3 pointer to stack
;
LW a0, 0x0084 (sp) ;load character 3 drink amount ptr from stack
SW a0, 0x001C (sp) ;store character 3 drink amount ptr to stack
;
LW a0, 0x0088 (sp) ;load character 4 pointer from stack
SW a0, 0x0020 (sp) ;store character 4 pointer to stack
;
LW a0, 0x008C (sp) ;load character 4 pointer from stack
SW a0, 0x0024 (sp) ;store character 4 pointer to stack
;
SW r0, 0x0028 (sp) ;terminate sprintf
;
LI a0, 0x800977C0 ;where to store result
LUI a1, hi(DrinkPrintingFormatters)
ADDIU a1, a1, lo(DrinkPrintingFormatters) ;ptr to format to use
JAL sprintf
NOP

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex
NOP
MOVE S4 V0

LUI S1 hi(0x800CD0A5) ; First RAM address with Item
ADDIU S1 S1 lo(0x800CD0A5)
LI S0 0 ; Loop Counter

drinkdisplayloop:
LI T3 3

NOP

LI T0 -1 ; 0xFF

BEQ T0 T2 drinkdisplayloop_exit ; if 0xFF, exit
NOP

MOVE A0 S4

LI T1 -1

CopyPlayerDrinkAmounts: ;copy drink amounts from board ram to
;label PlayerDrinkAmounts
ADDIU sp, sp, -0x20
SW t0, 0x0010 (sp)
SW v0, 0x0014 (sp) ;counter
SW s0, 0x0018 (sp) ;pointer to read from
SW s1, 0x001C (sp) ;pointer to store to
LI s0, 0x800CD0A1 ;pointer to drinks (big hardcode)
LUI s1, hi(PlayerDrinkAmounts)
ADDIU s1, s1, lo(PlayerDrinkAmounts)
ORI v0, r0, 0x0000 ;init counter
DrinkAmountLoop:
LBU t0, 0x0000 (s0) ;load current drink amount
ADDIU t0, t0, 0x0030 ;convert int to string
SB t0, 0x0000 (s1) ;store current drink
ADDIU s0, s0, 0x0001 ;add 1 to drink pointer
ADDIU s1, s1, 0x0002 ;add 2 to PlayerDrinkAmountsPointer
ADDIU v0, v0, 0x0001 ;add 1 to counter
SLTI t0, v0, 0x0004 ;exit if v1 is equal to v0
BNEZ t0, DrinkAmountLoop
NOP
LW t0, 0x0010 (sp)
LW v0, 0x0014 (sp)
LW s0, 0x0018 (sp)
LW s1, 0x001C (sp)
JR RA
ADDIU sp, sp, 0x20

[GG] Magic Bridge.code:
; NAME: [GG] Magic Bridge
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: Space|BridgeStart
; PARAM: Space|BridgeEnd

ADDIU SP SP -80
SW RA 76(SP)
SW S0 72(SP)
SW S1 68(SP)
SW S2 64(SP)
SW S4 60(SP)
SW S5 56(SP)
SW S6 52(SP)



JAL GetPlayerStruct ; at V0
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
MOVE S4 V0

LI T0 0x800CD0A0 ; Magic Bridge Space Index Address
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Load Magic Bridge Space Index Value

LI T2 1 ; Blue Space Index
BEQL T1 T2 adjustcoins
LI S2 6 ; Add 6 Coins
LI T2 2 ; Red Space Index
BEQL T1 T2 adjustcoins
LI S2 -6 ; Subtract 6 Coins
LI T2 4 ; Happening Space Index
BEQ T1 T2 happeningevent
NOP
LI T2 7 ; Bank Space Index
BEQ T1 T2 bankevent
NOP
J exit
NOP

adjustcoins:
LUI T0 hi(cur_player_spaces_remaining)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(cur_player_spaces_remaining)
LWU T1 0(T0) ; Load spaces remaining into T1

BNEZ T1 exit ; exit if there's no spaces remaining
NOP

LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 -1 ; Idle Animation
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A2 2 ; Loop

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
JAL AdjustPlayerCoinsGradual
ADDU A1 R0 S2 ; Coins

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
JAL ShowPlayerCoinChange
ADDU A1 R0 S2 ; Coins

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 30 ; Frames

J exit
NOP

NOP

LBU T1 16(S4) ; Current Player's Chain Space Index

MOVE A0 T0
JAL GetAbsSpaceIndexFromChainSpaceIndex ; at V0
MOVE A1 T1

LI T2 BridgeStart
BNE V0 T2 subtractcoins ; No greeting if it's not the first space of the bridge
NOP

SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
LI A0 2 ; Character image (Koopa)
LUI A1 hi(BankGreeting_Message)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(BankGreeting_Message)
LI A2 0
JAL ShowMessage
LI A3 0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL CloseMessage
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

subtractcoins:
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
JAL AdjustPlayerCoinsGradual
SUBU A1 R0 S2 ; Coins

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
JAL ShowPlayerCoinChange
SUBU A1 R0 S2 ; Coins

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 15 ; Frames

LUI T0 hi(bank_coin_total)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(bank_coin_total) 
LHU T1 0(T0) ; Load Bank Coin Total

ADDU S1 S2 T1 ; Add to get new Bank Coin Total
SH S1 0(T0) ; Store new Bank Coin Total

LBU T0 15(S4) ; Current Player's Chain Index
LBU T1 16(S4) ; Current Player's Chain Space Index

MOVE A0 T0
JAL GetAbsSpaceIndexFromChainSpaceIndex ; at V0
MOVE A1 T1

LI T2 BridgeStart
BEQ V0 T2 banktotalannouncement ; Announce if it's the first space of the bridge
NOP
LI T2 BridgeEnd
BNE V0 T2 exit ; No Bank total announcement if it's not the last space of the bridge
NOP

banktotalannouncement:
LUI A0 hi(TotalDrinkCount_String)
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(TotalDrinkCount_String) ; Parse Destination
LUI A1 hi(percent_d)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(percent_d) ; String Format
MOVE A2 S1 ; Value to convert
JAL sprintf
LI A3 0

SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
LI A0 2 ; Character image (Koopa)
LUI A1 hi(BankGreeting2_Message)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(BankGreeting2_Message)
LUI A2 hi(TotalDrinkCount_String)
ADDIU A2 A2 lo(TotalDrinkCount_String)
JAL ShowMessage
LI A3 0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL CloseMessage
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP
J exit
NOP

nocoinsinbank:
SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
LI A0 2 ; Character image (Koopa)
LUI A1 hi(NoCoinsInBank_Message)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(NoCoinsInBank_Message)
LI A2 0
JAL ShowMessage
LI A3 0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL CloseMessage
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP
J exit
NOP


exit:
LW RA 76(SP)
LW S0 72(SP)
LW S1 68(SP)
LW S2 64(SP)
LW S4 60(SP)
LW S5 56(SP)
LW S6 52(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80

.asciiz "%d"

[GG] Tower of Power.code:
; NAME: [GG] Tower of Power
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: Space|SpaceToFace
; PARAM: Space|Destination
; PARAM: Space|NextSpace
; PARAM: Space|PreviousSpace

ADDIU SP SP -120
SW RA 116(SP)
SW S0 112(SP)
SW S1 108(SP) ; Current Player's Page Count Value
SW S2 104(SP) ; Current Player's Page Count Address
SW S3 100(SP)
SW S4 96(SP) ; Current Player's Struct
SW S5 92(SP) ; Page Count Address 
SW S6 88(SP)
SW S7 84(SP)
SW FP 80(SP)



START:
JAL RefreshOptionArray
NOP


LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 -1 ; Idle Animation
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A3 2 ; Loop

LI A0 -1 ; Current Player's Index
LI A1 8 ; Frames it takes to turn
LI A2 SpaceToFace
JAL 0x800ED20C ; RotatePlayerModel
NOP

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 8

JAL GetPlayerStruct ; at V0
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
MOVE S4 V0 ; copy to S4

LI S5 0x800CD096 ; Page Count Address
LB T1 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index

ADDU S2 S5 T1 ; Add to get Current Player's Page Count Address
LBU S1 0(S2) ; Load Current Player's Page Count

SLTI T3 S1 5 ; ON IF Player doesn't have enough Pages
BNEZ T3 inactivemessage 
NOP

firstprompt:
JAL GetColorFormatter
NOP ; returns color for 2nd and 3rd option on V0, V1, and T0-3

LUI A0 hi(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
ADDIU A0 A0 lo(A_Pointer_with_enough_space) ; Parse Destination
LUI A1 hi(ToPWelcome_Prompt)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(ToPWelcome_Prompt) ; String Format
MOVE A2 V0 ; 1st Option Color
MOVE A3 V1 ; 2nd Option Color
SW T0 16(SP) ; 3rd Option Color
SW T1 20(SP) ; 4th Option Color
SW T2 24(SP) ; 5th Option Color
SW T3 28(SP) ; 6th Option Color
JAL sprintf ; Creates String 
SW R0 32(SP) ; Terminator

SW R0 16(SP)
SW R0 20(SP)
SW R0 24(SP)
LI A0 -1 ; (None)
LUI A1 hi(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(A_Pointer_with_enough_space)
LI A2 0
JAL ShowMessage
LI A3 0

JAL DisableOptions ; A0 has Window ID
NOP

JAL GetAIChoice
NOP
SW V1 76(SP) ; Next Prompt's choice, if any

LI A0 2 ; Pick whatever is in A1 as AI's Choice
JAL GetBasicPromptSelection
MOVE A1 V0 ; 
MOVE S0 V0 ; Chosen answer at S0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL CloseMessage
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

BEQZ S0 magicstrike
NOP
LI T0 1
BEQ S0 T0 halloweenparty
NOP
LI T0 2
BEQ S0 T0 bonusbogus
NOP
LI T0 3
BEQ S0 T0 itembagdeluxe
NOP
LI T0 4
BEQ S0 T0 cashswap
NOP
LI T0 5
BEQ S0 T0 stellarexchange
NOP
LI T0 6
BEQ S0 T0 spellexplanations
NOP
LI T0 7
BEQ S0 T0 exit
NOP
JAL ViewBoardMap
NOP
J firstprompt
NOP

;======================================================================================MAGIC STRIKE
magicstrike:
LI A0 0 ; Bar Code Fadeout
JAL InitFadeOut
LI A1 16 ; Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 16 ; Frames

JAL PlaySound
ADDIU A0 R0 0x153 ; Curse sound

LI T1 5
SUBU S1 S1 T1 ; Subtract 5 Pages
SB S1 0(S2) ; Store new number of Pages

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x1D1 ; Page Subtract Sound

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 30 ; Frames

LI S0 0 ; Start with Player 1
magicstrikeloop:
LI T0 4 ; All players affected
BEQ S0 T0 magicstrikeloop_exit ; exit when everyone's affected
NOP
LBU T0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
BEQ S0 T0 magicstrikeloop_add1 ; branch if checking current player
NOP
JAL CheckMagicVeil
MOVE A0 S0 ; Player Index
BNEZ V0 magicstrikeloop_add1 ; branch if player is under Magic Veil
NOP
ADDU T1 S5 S0 ; Add index to get this player's Current Pages address
LBU T2 0(T1) ; Load Player's Page Value
LI T3 5 ; Reduce by 5
SUBU T2 T2 T3
BLTZL T2 magicstrikeloopstore
LI T2 0 ; Make it 0 if negative

magicstrikeloopstore:
SB T2 0(T1) ; Store 

MOVE A0 S0 ; Player Index
JAL PlayVoice
LI A1 1 ; Sad Voice
JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 20 ; Frames


magicstrikeloop_add1:
J magicstrikeloop
ADDIU S0 S0 1 ; Add 1 to check next player

magicstrikeloop_exit:
LI A0 0 ; Bar Code Fadeout
JAL InitFadeIn
LI A1 16 ; Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 21 ; Frames

J exit
NOP

;===================================================================================HALLOWEEN PARTY
halloweenparty:
LI T1 5
SUBU S1 S1 T1 ; Subtract 5 Pages
SB S1 0(S2) ; Store new number of Pages

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x1D1 ; Page Subtract Sound

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 30 ; Frames

JAL PlayMusic
LI A0 0x4A ; Sound Config

LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 6 ; Star Get Animation
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A2 2 ; Loop

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 90 ; Frames

LI A0 1 ; Circle Fadeout
JAL InitFadeOut
LI A1 16 ; Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 21 ; Frames

JAL PlaySound 
LI A0 0x107 ; Warp Block Sound Index

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 15 ; Frames

LI S0 0 ; Start with Current Player
LI S7 0xc1a00000 ; -20 Float
halloweenparty_loop:
LI T0 4 ; All players affected
BEQ S0 T0 halloweenparty_exit ; exit when everyone's affected
NOP
LBU T0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
BEQ S0 T0 halloweenparty_add1 ; branch if checking current player
NOP
JAL CheckMagicVeil
MOVE A0 S0 ; Player Index
BNEZ V0 halloweenparty_add1 ; branch if player is under Magic Veil
NOP

JAL GetPlayerStruct
MOVE A0 S0 
MOVE S6 V0 ; Copy to S6

LBU A0 29(S6) ; Assigns Current Player Index to A0
LI A1 Destination_chain_index ; Assigns Chain Index to A1
JAL SetPlayerOntoChain
LI A2 Destination_chain_space_index ; Assigns Space Index to A2

LBU A0 29(S6) ; Assigns Current Player Index to A0
LI A1 PreviousSpace_chain_index ; Assigns Chain Index to A1
JAL SetPrevChainAndSpace
LI A2 PreviousSpace_chain_space_index ; Assigns Space Index to A2

LBU A0 29(S6) ; Assigns Current Player Index to A0
LI A1 NextSpace_chain_index ; Assigns Chain Index to A1
JAL SetNextChainAndSpace
LI A2 NextSpace_chain_space_index ; Assigns Space Index to A2

LI A0 Destination_chain_index
JAL GetAbsSpaceIndexFromChainSpaceIndex ; Gets True Space Index at V0
LI A1 Destination_chain_space_index

JAL GetSpaceData ; Pointer to Space Data at V0
MOVE A0 V0 ; True Space Index

LW V1 8(V0) ; X pos of Space
MOVE T0 V1 ; Copy to T0
LI T2 0x40a00000 ; Float value for 5
MTC1 T2 F0 ; Move Float to F1
MTC1 S7 F1 ; Move Space X Pos float to F1
ADD.S F0 F1 F0 ; Add the floats for maximum floatiness
MFC1 S7 F0
MTC1 T0 F1 ; Move Space X Pos float to F1
ADD.S F3 F1 F0 ; Add the floats for maximum floatiness
MFC1 T0 F3 ; Move to new X pos to T0

LW V1 16(V0) ; Y pos of Space
MOVE T1 V1 ; Copy to T1

LI T2 0x41200000 ; Float value for -10
MTC1 T2 F0 ; Move Float to F1
MTC1 T1 F1 ; Move Space Y Pos float to F1
ADD.S F0 F1 F0 ; Add the floats for maximum floatiness
MFC1 T1 F0 ; Move total to T1

LW V1 0x24(S6) ; Pointer to player Coords
SW T0 12(V1) ; Write into player's X Coords

ADDIU V1 V1 8 ; This should load current player's Y Coords
SW T1 20(V1) ; Write into player's Y Coords

LB A0 29(S6) ; Player Index
JAL PlayVoice
LI A1 1 ; Happy Voice

JAL SleepProcess 
LI A0 20 ; Sleeps for 20 frames

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 A0 ; Shift Left by Player Index 

LUI T3 hi(0x800CD0AF)
ADDIU T3 T3 lo(0x800CD0AF) ; Cursed Dice Flag Address
LBU T4 0(T3) ; Flag Value
LBU T2 29(S6) ; This player's Index
LI T5 1 
SLLV T6 T5 T2 ; Shift left by player's index
AND V0 T4 T6 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Curse is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ V0 halloweenparty_add1
NOP

LI T5 1
SLLV T5 T5 T2 ; Shift by the player's index
ADDU T4 T4 T5 ; Add to current flag value
SB T4 0(T3)

LI T0 2 ; Poison Mushroom png 
LBU T1 23(S6) ; This player's Status Flags
ADDU T1 T0 T1 ; Add Poison Mushroom png
SB T1 23(S6) ; This player's Status Flags

;LBU A0 29(S6) ; This player's Index
;JAL 0x80114FC0 ; Spawn Curse Heads?
;LI A1 2 ; Slow Curse

;JAL 0x801150C0 ; Rotate Head
;LBU A0 29(S6) ; This player's Index


halloweenparty_add1:
J halloweenparty_loop
ADDIU S0 S0 1

halloweenparty_exit:
LUI T0 hi(cur_player_spaces_remaining)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(cur_player_spaces_remaining) ; Address on T0
LW T1 0(T0) 
ADDIU T1 T1 3 ; Add 3 to player's remaining roll
SW T1 0(T0)

LUI T3 hi(0x800CDBD2)
ADDIU T3 T3 lo(0x800CDBD2) ; P1 Forced Roll Address

LI T2 0x4C ; Distance between each player's addresses
LBU T4 29(S4) ; Player Index
MULT T4 T2 ; Multiply Current Player Index by T2
MFLO T2 ; Move Result to T2
ADDU T3 T3 T2 ; Add to get current Player's Forced Roll address
SB T1 3(T3) 

LI A0 0 ; Bar Code Fadeout
JAL InitFadeIn
LI A1 16 ; Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 16 ; Frames

LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayVoice
LI A1 0 ; Happy Voice

JAL SleepProcess 
LI A0 30 ; Sleeps for 30 frames

JAL GetBoardAudioIndex
NOP

JAL PlayMusic
MOVE A0 V0 ; Return music to normal

J exit
NOP

;===================================================================================ITEM BAG DELUXE
itembagdeluxe:
LI T1 7
SUBU S1 S1 T1 ; Subtract 7 Pages
SB S1 0(S2) ; Store new number of Pages

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x1D1 ; Page Subtract Sound

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 30 ; Frames

ADDIU S3 S4 24 ; Item 1 Address
LI S0 3 ; Loops
megaitembag_loop:
JAL GetRandomByte ; 0-255 at V0
NOP
LI T0 7 ; Total Number of Items
DIVU V0 T0 ; MOD 7
MFHI V0 ; Remainder at V0 (0-6)
LUI T0 hi(MegaItemBag_Array)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(MegaItemBag_Array)
ADDU V0 T0 V0 ; Add Remainder to get correct Item Index spot in Array
LBU V0 0(V0) ; Load Item Index 

SB V0 0(S3)
ADDIU S3 S3 1 ; Add 1 for next Item Address
ADDIU S0 S0 -1 ; Subtract 1 from Loop count 

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x11C ; Item obtained sfx

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 45 ; Frames

BNEZ S0 megaitembag_loop
NOP

JAL PlayMusic
LI A0 0x68

LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 6 ; Star Get Animation
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A2 0 ; Don't loop

LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayVoice
LI A1 0 ; Happy Voice

JAL SleepProcess 
LI A0 90 ; Sleeps for 90 frames

JAL GetBoardAudioIndex
NOP

JAL PlayMusic
MOVE A0 V0 ; Return music to normal

J exit
NOP

GetAIChoice:
ADDIU SP SP -80
SW RA 76(SP)

NOP

NOP

SLTI T0 S1 8 ; ON IF 0-7 Pages
BNEZ T0 AICheckCashSwap
NOP

JAL GetPlayerPlacement ; at V0
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Player's Index

LI T0 3 ; 4th Place 
BNE V0 T0 AICheckCashSwap ; Branch IF not 4th Place
NOP

JAL GetPlayerPlacement
LI A0 0 ; Check Player 1 

BEQZ V0 AIStellarExchangeVeilCheck ; Branch if they're in 1st Place
LI A0 0

JAL GetPlayerPlacement
LI A0 1 ; Check Player 2

BEQZ V0 AIStellarExchangeVeilCheck ; Branch if they're in 1st Place
LI A0 1

JAL GetPlayerPlacement
LI A0 2 ; Check Player 3

BEQZ V0 AIStellarExchangeVeilCheck ; Branch if they're in 1st Place
LI A0 2

LI A0 3 ; Player 4 is in 1st Place

JAL CheckMagicVeil
NOP

BNEZ V0 AICheckCashSwap
NOP

LI V0 5 ; Stellar Exchange index
J GetAIChoice_exit
MOVE V1 A0 ; Player Index to target on next prompt

SLTI T0 S1 7 ; ON IF 0-6 Pages
BNEZ T0 AICheckMegaItemBag
NOP

CashSwapP1:
LI T0 0 
LBU T1 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
BEQ T1 T0 CashSwapP2
NOP

JAL GetPlayerStruct
LI A0 0 ; Player 1

LHU T0 10(V0) ; P1 Coins
LHU T1 10(S4) ; Current Player's Coins
SUBU T2 T0 T1 ; Subtract Current player's coins from P1 Coins

SLTI T3 T2 50 ; ON IF 0-49
BNEZ T3 CashSwapP2
NOP

LI V0 4 ; Cash Swap Index
J GetAIChoice_exit
LI V1 0 ; Index of player to select on next prompt


CashSwapP2:
LI T0 1
LBU T1 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
BEQ T1 T0 CashSwapP3
NOP

JAL GetPlayerStruct
LI A0 1 ; Player 1

LHU T0 10(V0) ; P1 Coins
LHU T1 10(S4) ; Current Player's Coins
SUBU T2 T0 T1 ; Subtract Current player's coins from P1 Coins

SLTI T3 T2 50 ; ON IF 0-49
BNEZ T3 CashSwapP3
NOP

LI V0 4 ; Cash Swap Index
J GetAIChoice_exit
LI V1 1 ; Index of player to select on next prompt

LBU T1 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
BEQ T1 T0 CashSwapP4
NOP

JAL GetPlayerStruct
LI A0 2 ; Player 1

LHU T0 10(V0) ; P1 Coins
LHU T1 10(S4) ; Current Player's Coins
SUBU T2 T0 T1 ; Subtract Current player's coins from P1 Coins

SLTI T3 T2 50 ; ON IF 0-49
BNEZ T3 CashSwapP4
NOP

BEQ T1 T0 AICheckMegaItemBag
NOP

LHU T0 10(V0) ; P1 Coins
LHU T1 10(S4) ; Current Player's Coins

NOP

BNEZ T0 AICheckBonusBogus

NOP

NOP

LI V0 2 ; Bonus Bogus Index

SLTI T0 S1 5 ; ON IF 0-4 Pages
BNEZ T0 AICheckMagicStrike
NOP
LUI T0 hi(current_star_spawn)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(current_star_spawn) ; Address of current Star Spawn Cycle
ADDIU T1 T0 1 ; Address of first Star Spawn Index in the Cycle
LBU T0 0(T0) ; Load Index of Star Spawn to T0
ADDU T0 T0 T1 ; Add to get address of current Star Spawn Index
LBU T2 0(T0) ; Load current Star Spawn Index to T2

BEQL T2 R0 GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 1 ; Halloween Party Index
LI T0 1
BEQL T2 T0 GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 1 ; Halloween Party Index
LI T0 2
BEQL T2 T0 GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 1 ; Halloween Party Index
LI T0 7
BEQL T2 T0 GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 1 ; Halloween Party Index

AICheckMagicStrike:
SLTI T0 S1 5 ; ON IF 0-4 Pages
BNEZL T0 GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 6 ; Choose Nothing Index

LI T4 0x800CD096
LI T5 0 ; Start Page Count at 0
LBU T3 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
BEQZ T3 checkplayer2
NOP

LI T1 1 
SLL T2 T1 0 ; Shift Left by Player 1 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer2
NOP

LBU T5 0(T4) ; Player 1's Page Count
checkplayer2:
LI T4 0x800CD097 ; Check Player 2's Pages
LI T6 1
BEQ T3 T6 checkplayer3
NOP

LI T1 1 
SLL T2 T1 1 ; Shift Left by Player 2 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer3
NOP

LBU T9 0(T4) ; Player 2's Page Value
ADDU T5 T5 T9 ; Add Total
checkplayer3:
LI T4 0x800CD098 ; Check Player 3's Pages
LI T6 2
BEQ T3 T6 checkplayer4
NOP

LI T1 1 
SLL T2 T1 2 ; Shift Left by Player 3 Index 
LI A1 0x800CD09C ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU A2 0(A1) ; Flag Value
AND A3 A2 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkplayer4
NOP

LBU T9 0(T4) ; Player 3's Page Value
ADDU T5 T5 T9 ; Add Total

; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.
BNEZ A3 checkfor5pagestotal
NOP

LBU T9 0(T4) ; Player 4's Page Value
ADDU T5 T5 T9 ; Add Total

checkfor5pagestotal:
SLTI T2 T5 10 ; ON IF 0 - 9
BNEZL T2 GetAIChoice_exit
LI V0 7 ; Choose Nothing Index

LI V0 0 ; Magic Strike Index

GetAIChoice_exit:
LW RA 76(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80

[GG] Dicey Junctions check.code:
; NAME: [GG] Dicey Junctions check
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: Space|Left
; PARAM: Space|Right

ADDIU SP SP -80
SW RA 76(SP)
SW S4 72(SP)
SW S3 68(SP)
SW S2 64(SP)
SW S0 60(SP)


LI S0 0

JAL GetPlayerStruct
LI A0 -1
MOVE S4 V0 

LBU T4 23(S4) ; Status Flags
ANDI T0 T4 0x80 
BNEZ T0 exit ; exit if player is in reverse
NOP

LBU T0 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 T0 ; Shift Left by Player Index 

LUI S2 hi(0x800CD09A)
ADDIU S2 S2 lo(0x800CD09A) ; Dicey Junction Flag Address
LBU T4 0(S2) ; Flag Value

AND T1 T4 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index

LI S3 50 ; 50/50 
BNEZL T1 diceyjunctions ; Branch
LI S0 1 ; Flag for removing Dicey Junction Flag

J exit
NOP

JAL PlayerIsCPU
LI A0 -1 

BEQZ V0 exit ; If 0, exit because it's a human
NOP

LBU S3 1(S4) ; Load CPU's Difficulty (0-3)

LBU T1 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index

LUI T0 hi(0x800CD0A1)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(0x800CD0A1) ; Drink Count Address
ADDU T0 T0 T1 ; T0 now holds current player's drink count address
LBU T2 0(T0) ; T2 now holds current player's drink count value

SLTI T3 T2 4 ; ON IF Player has 3 or less drinks
BNEZ T3 LeftChoice
NOP

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayerHasCoins ; 
LI A1 20 ; Coins

BNEZ V0 checkstar ; Check Star Location if 20 Coins or more
NOP

checkspacesremaining:
LUI T0 hi(cur_player_spaces_remaining)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(cur_player_spaces_remaining) ; Address of spaces remaining
LW T0 0(T0) ; Load Value


LI T1 3
BEQ T0 T1 checkitems
NOP
LI T1 7
BEQ T0 T1 checkfor20coins
NOP
LI T1 9
BEQ T0 T1 checkfor0coins
NOP
J exit
NOP

checkstar:
LUI T0 hi(current_star_spawn)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(current_star_spawn) ; Address of current Star Spawn Cycle
ADDIU T1 T0 1 ; Address of first Star Spawn Index in the Cycle
LBU T0 0(T0) ; Load Index of Star Spawn to T0
ADDU T0 T0 T1 ; Add to get address of current Star Spawn Index
LBU T2 0(T0) ; Load current Star Spawn Index to T2

LI T9 7
BEQ T2 T9 LeftChoice ; Branch IF it's Star 07
NOP
J checkspacesremaining
NOP

checkbank:
LUI T0 hi(bank_coin_total)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(bank_coin_total) ; Address of current bank total
LH T0 0(T0) ; Load Value

SLTI T1 T0 10 ; ON IF Bank has less than 10 coins
BNEZ T1 RightChoice
NOP
J LeftChoice
NOP

checkitems:
JAL PlayerHasEmptyItemSlot
LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
LUI T1 hi(0xFFFFFFFF)
ADDIU T1 T1 lo(0xFFFFFFFF) ; No Item Value
BNE V0 T1 LeftChoice ; Left if full
NOP
J checkbank
NOP

checkfor20coins:
LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayerHasCoins
LI A1 20

BEQZ V0 LeftChoice ; Pick Left if no coins 
NOP
J RightChoice
NOP

checkfor0coins:
LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayerHasCoins
LI A1 1

BEQZ V0 RightChoice ; Pick Left if no coins 
NOP
J LeftChoice
NOP

LeftChoice:
BEQZ S3 CalculateChance
LI A0 50 ; 50%
LI T9 1 ; Normal Difficulty
BEQ S3 T9 CalculateChance
LI A0 30 ; 30%
LI T9 2 ; Hard Difficulty
BEQ S3 T9 CalculateChance
LI A0 3 ; 3%
J CalculateChance
LI A0 0 ; 0% Super Hard Difficulty

RightChoice:
BEQZ S3 CalculateChance
LI A0 50 ; 50%
LI T9 1 ; Normal Difficulty
BEQ S3 T9 CalculateChance
LI A0 70 ; 70%
LI T9 2 ; Hard Difficulty
BEQ S3 T9 CalculateChance
LI A0 97 ; 97%

LI A0 100 ; 100% Super Hard Difficulty 
J CalculateChance
NOP

diceyjunctions:
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 4 ; Dizzy Animation
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A2 2 ; Don't loop

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0xC2 ; Dizzy Sound effect

LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayVoice
LI A1 1 ; Sad Voice

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 45 ; Frames


CalculateChance:
JAL RNGPercentChance ; 0 = Left - 1 = Right
NOP 

BNEZ V0 GoRight
NOP

LI A1 Left_chain_index
J SetDecision
LI A2 Left_chain_space_index

GoRight:
LI A1 Right_chain_index
LI A2 Right_chain_space_index

SetDecision:
JAL SetNextChainAndSpace
LBU A0 29(S4)

BEQZ S0 exit
NOP

LBU T0 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 T0 ; Shift Left by Player Index 
LBU T4 0(S2) ; Flag Value

SUBU T4 T4 T2 ; Subtract
SB T4 0(S2) ; Store new Flag Value


exit:
LW S0 60(SP)
LW S2 64(SP)
LW S3 68(SP)
LW S4 72(SP)
LW RA 76(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80

.align 16
; A0 = Player's Index
; A1 = Happy/Sad Index
PlayVoice:
ADDIU SP SP -32
SW RA 28(SP)

JAL GetPlayerStruct
NOP

LBU T0 3(V0) ; Character Index

BNEZ A1 sad
NOP

happy:
JAL PlaySound
ADDIU A0 T0 0x275 ; Mario's Happy Voice Index
J PlayVoice_exit
NOP

sad:
JAL PlaySound
ADDIU A0 T0 0x287

PlayVoice_exit:
LW RA 28(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 32

[GG] Zap Wire check.code:
; NAME: [GG] Zap Wire check
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct

ADDIU SP SP -80
SW RA 76(SP)
SW S4 72(SP) ; Current Player Struct



JAL GetPlayerStruct
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
MOVE S4 V0 ; Copy to S4

LBU A0 15(S4)
JAL GetAbsSpaceIndexFromChainSpaceIndex ; True Index at V0
LBU A1 16(S4)

LUI T0 hi(0x800CD09F)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(0x800CD09F)
LBU T2 0(T0) ; Load Index of Zap Wire Space

BNE V0 T2 exit
NOP

JAL CheckMagicVeil
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index

BNEZ V0 activeveil
NOP

LI T1 0x00 ; No Space
SB T1 0(T0) ; Delete Zap Wire

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x4B0 ; Zap sfx

LBU T0 3(S4) ; Character Index
JAL PlaySound
ADDIU A0 T0 0x287 ; Add Mario's Despair Voice Index

LI A0 -1 ; Current player's index
LI A1 4 ; Dizzy Animation
JAL 0x800F2304 ; CueAnimation
LI A2 2 ; Loop

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 15

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
JAL AdjustPlayerCoinsGradual
LI A1 -20 ; Subtract 20 Coins

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
JAL ShowPlayerCoinChange
LI A1 -20 ; Subtract 20 Coins

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 30

SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
LI A0 -1 ; Character image (None)
LUI A1 hi(ZapWire_Message)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(ZapWire_Message)
LI A2 0
JAL ShowMessage
LI A3 0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL CloseMessage
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

J exit
NOP

activeveil:
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 -1 ; Idle Animation
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A2 2 ; Don't loop

SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
LI A0 -1 ; Character image (None)
LUI A1 hi(ZapWireVeil_Message)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(ZapWireVeil_Message)
LI A2 0
JAL ShowMessage
LI A3 0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL CloseMessage
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

exit: 
LW S4 72(SP) ; Current Player Struct
LW RA 76(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80

.align 16
CheckMagicVeil:
; A0 = Player Index
ADDIU SP SP -40
SW RA 36(SP)

LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 A0 ; Shift Left by Player Index 

LUI T3 hi(0x800CD09C)
ADDIU T3 T3 lo(0x800CD09C) ; Magic Veil Protection Flag Address
LBU T4 0(T3) ; Flag Value

AND V0 T4 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Magic Veil is not active, 1 if it is.

LW RA 36(SP)
JR RA

.ascii "Electricity continues to course through this space\x85\xFF\x00"

[GG] Status Messages.code:
; NAME: [GG] Status Messages
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct

ADDIU SP SP -80
SW RA 76(SP)
SW S4 72(SP)

JAL GetPlayerStruct ; at V0
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
MOVE S4 V0 ; Copy to S4

LI T0 0x800CD0A5 ; Everyone is CPU Player Turns Address
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Load Player Turns remaining
BEQZ T1 checkdiceyjunctions ; Nobody needs to be a CPU
NOP
ADDIU T1 T1 -1 ; Subtract 1 from Turns Remaining
SB T1 0(T0) ; Store Turns Remaining
BNEZ T1 checkdiceyjunctions ; exit if the counter still isn't 0
NOP
LI S0 0 ; Start with Player 1
everyoneisCPUloop:
LI T1 4 ; All Players Checked
BEQ S0 T1 everyoneisCPUloopexit ; exit once everyone is checked
NOP
LI T0 0x800CD0A6 ; Who is Human Address
LBU T2 0(T0) ; Who is Human Flag
LI T3 1 ; bit flag
SLLV T4 T3 S0 ; Shift Left by Player Index
AND T5 T4 T2 ; 0 if CPU
BEQL T5 R0 everyoneisCPUloop ; loop if it's a CPU
ADDIU S0 S0 1 ; Add 1 to check next player

JAL GetPlayerStruct ; at V0
MOVE A0 S0 ; Player Index

LI T0 4
SB T0 4(V0) ; Make Player Human
J everyoneisCPUloop
ADDIU S0 S0 1

everyoneisCPUloopexit:
LI T0 0x800CD0A6 ; Who is Human Address
SB R0 0(T0) ; Delete Who is Human flags

LUI A1 hi(EveryoneIsCPUAlert_Message)
JAL ShowMessage_Function
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(EveryoneIsCPUAlert_Message)

checkdiceyjunctions:
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 A0 ; Shift Left by Player Index 

LUI T3 hi(0x800CD09A)
ADDIU T3 T3 lo(0x800CD09A) ; Dicey Junctions Flag Address
LBU T4 0(T3) ; Flag Value

AND V0 T4 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Curse is not active, 1 if it is.
BEQZ V0 checkitemlock
NOP

LUI A1 hi(DiceyJunctionsAlert_Message)
JAL ShowMessage_Function
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(DiceyJunctionsAlert_Message)


checkitemlock:
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 A0 ; Shift Left by Player Index 

LUI T3 hi(0x800CD0A2)
ADDIU T3 T3 lo(0x800CD0A2) ; Item Lock Flag Address
LBU T4 0(T3) ; Flag Value

AND V0 T4 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Item Lock is not active, 1 if it is.
BEQZ V0 checkitemlock2 ; Either a turn hasn't passed or Item Lock is not active
NOP

LI T1 1
LBU T0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
SLLV T2 T1 T0 ; Shift bit Left by Player's Index
LUI T4 hi(0x800CD0A2)
ADDIU T4 T4 lo(0x800CD0A2) ; Item Lock Turn Count Flag Address
LBU T5 0(T4)
SUBU T3 T5 T2 ; Turn bit flag off
SB T3 0(T4) ; Store new flag value

LUI T4 hi(0x800CD09B)
ADDIU T4 T4 lo(0x800CD09B) ; Item Lock Flag Address
LBU T5 0(T4)
SUBU T3 T5 T2 ; Turn bit flag off
SB T3 0(T4) ; Store new flag value

J exit
NOP


checkitemlock2:
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 A0 ; Shift Left by Player Index 

LUI T3 hi(0x800CD09B)
ADDIU T3 T3 lo(0x800CD09B) ; Item Lock Flag Address
LBU T4 0(T3) ; Flag Value

AND V0 T4 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index
; V0 returns 0 if not Curse is not active, 1 if it is.
BEQZ V0 exit
NOP

LUI A1 hi(ItemLockAlert_Message)
JAL ShowMessage_Function
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(ItemLockAlert_Message)

LUI T4 hi(0x800CD0A9)
ADDIU T4 T4 lo(0x800CD0A9) ; Item Use Flag Address
LI T1 1 ; can't use item

SB T1 0(T4) ; store flag

LI T1 1 
LBU T5 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index
SLLV T2 T1 T5 ; Shift Left by Chosen Player Index 
LUI T3 hi(0x800CD0A2)
ADDIU T3 T3 lo(0x800CD0A2) ; Item Lock Turn Count Flag Address
LBU T4 0(T3) ; Flag Value
ADDU T4 T4 T2 ; Add to get new flag value
SB T4 0(T3) ; Store new flag



exit:
LW S4 72(SP)
LW RA 76(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80


.align 16
ShowMessage_Function:
ADDIU SP SP -80
SW RA 76(SP)

SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
LI A0 -1 ; Character image (None)
LI A2 0
JAL 0x800EC8EC ; ShowMessage
LI A3 0

JAL 0x800EC9DC
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6C8
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

LW RA 76(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80

DiceyJunctionsAlert_Message:
.ascii "\x05Dicey Junctions\x08 will make your next\x0A"
.ascii "junction decision be completely random\x85\x0A"
.ascii "\x5DMagic Veil will not undo this effect\x5E\xFF\x00"
