[GG] Hidden Vlock.code:
; NAME: [GG] Hidden Vlock
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct

ADDIU SP SP -80
SW RA 76(SP)
SW S4 72(SP)
SW S0 68(SP) 
SW S3 64(SP)

JAL GetPlayerStruct ; at V0
LI A0 -1
MOVE S4 V0 ; Copy to S4

LBU A0 15(S4) ; Chain Index
JAL GetAbsSpaceIndexFromChainSpaceIndex ; at V0
LBU A1 16(S4) ; Chain Space Index

LI T0 0x800CD0A4 ; Hidden Vlock Address
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Hidden Vlock Space Index

BNE V0 T1 exit ; exit if this space does not have a Hidden Vlock
NOP

JAL CheckMagicVeil
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index

BNEZ V0 exit ; exit if Current Player has Magic Veil active
NOP

J ztar
LI S0 50 ; Loop counter
rollvlock:
BEQZ S0 exit ; exit IF the player doesn't have anything they can lose
NOP 
JAL GetRandomByte ; 0-225 at V0
NOP
LI T0 3 ; 3 Types of Vlock, since Ztar is prioritized
DIVU V0 T0 
MFHI S3 ; 0-2

BEQZ S3 coins
NOP
LI T2 1
BEQ S3 T2 item
NOP
LI T2 2
BEQ S3 T2 pages
NOP

ztar:
LBU T0 14(S4) ; Stars 
BEQL T0 R0 rollvlock ; no stars, reroll
ADDIU S0 S0 -1 ; Subtract 1 from counter
J vlockconfirmed
NOP
ztar2:
LBU T0 14(S4) ; Stars 
ADDIU T0 T0 -1 ; Subtract 1 Star
SB T0 14(S4) 
JAL PlaySound
LI A0 283 ; Star Space Sound Index

J hiddenvlockending
NOP

coins:
LHU T0 10(S4) ; Coins
BEQL T0 R0 rollvlock ; no coins, reroll
ADDIU S0 S0 -1 ; Subtract 1 from counter
J vlockconfirmed
NOP
coins2:
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL AdjustPlayerCoinsGradual
LI A1 -20 ; Coins
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL ShowPlayerCoinChange
LI A1 -20 ; Coins

J hiddenvlockending
NOP

item:
LBU T0 24(S4) ; Item #1
LI T1 0xFF ; No Item
BEQL T0 T1 rollvlock ; no items, reroll
ADDIU S0 S0 -1 ; Subtract 1 from counter
J vlockconfirmed
NOP
item2:
ADDIU S0 S4 24 ; Add to get Item #1 address

itemslotroll:
JAL GetRandomByte ; 0-255 at V0
NOP
LI T0 3 
DIVU V0 T0 ; Divide by 3
MFHI T1
ADDU T2 S0 T1 ; Add to get proper Item Address
LBU T3 0(T2) ; Load Item Index
LI T4 0xFF ; No Item
BEQ T3 T4 itemslotroll ; no item in slot, reroll
NOP
SB T4 0(T2) ; Delete Item

JAL FixUpPlayerItemSlots
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player Index

JAL RefreshHUD
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player Index

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0xD ; Curse Mushroom Sound Effect

J hiddenvlockending
NOP

pages:
LI T0 0x800CD096 ; P1 Pages
LBU T1 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
ADDU T0 T0 T1 ; Current Player Pages Address
LBU T2 0(T0) ; Current Player Pages
BEQL T2 R0 rollvlock ; no pages, reroll
ADDIU S0 S0 -1 ; Subtract 1 from counter
J vlockconfirmed
NOP
pages2:
LI T0 0x800CD096 ; P1 Pages
LBU T1 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
ADDU T0 T0 T1 ; Current Player Pages Address
LBU T2 0(T0) ; Current Player Pages

ADDIU T2 T2 -3 ; Subtract 3 Pages
BLTZL T2 pages3
LI T2 0 ; If negative, make it 0

pages3:
SB T2 0(T0) ; Update Page Count

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x124 ; Red Space Sound Effect

J hiddenvlockending
NOP

vlockconfirmed:
JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x3A8 ; Hidden Block Sound Effect

LUI A1 hi(HiddenVlock_Message)
JAL ShowMessage_Function
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(HiddenVlock_Message)

BEQZ S3 coins2
NOP
LI T2 1
BEQ S3 T2 item2
NOP
LI T2 2
BEQ S3 T2 pages2
NOP
LI T2 3
BEQ S3 T2 ztar2
NOP

hiddenvlockending:
JAL PlayMusic
LI A0 113 ; Game Guy Lose Music

LBU T0 3(S4) ; Current Player's Character Index
JAL PlaySound
ADDIU A0 T0 0x287 ; Add Mario's Despair Voice Index

LI A0 -1 ; Current player's index
LI A1 3 ; Despair Animation
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A2 0

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 100 ; Frames

JAL GetBoardAudioIndex ; get original board music at V0
NOP

JAL PlayMusic ; play music index
MOVE A0 V0

LI T0 0x800CD0A4 ; Hidden Vlock Address
SB R0 0(T0) ; Delete Hidden Vlock

J exit
NOP



exit:
LW S0 68(SP) 
LW S3 64(SP)
LW S4 72(SP)
LW RA 76(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80


.align 16
ShowMessage_Function:
ADDIU SP SP -80
SW RA 76(SP)

SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
LI A0 -1 ; Character image (None)
LI A2 0
JAL 0x800EC8EC ; ShowMessage
LI A3 0

NOP
JAL 0x800EC6C8
NOP
JAL 0x800EC6EC
NOP

LW RA 76(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80

ADDIU SP SP -40

LUI T3 hi(0x800CD09C)

[GG] Boo.code:
; NAME: [GG] Boo
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: Space|BooSpace

ADDIU SP SP -80
SW RA 76(SP)
SW S4 72(SP)
SW S0 68(SP)


LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 -1 ; Idle Animation
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A2 2 ; Loop

JAL GetPlayerStruct ; at V0
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
MOVE S4 V0 ; Copy to S4

JAL PlayerHasEmptyItemSlot ; 0 if the first item slot is empty
LBU A0 29(S4)

BNEZ V0 offeringprompt ; If not 0, they have an item
NOP

SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
LI A0 -1 ; Character image (None)
LUI A1 hi(NoOffering_Message)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(NoOffering_Message)
LI A2 0
JAL ShowMessage 
LI A3 0

JAL CloseMessage_Function
NOP

NOP

offeringprompt:

BEQZ V0 nocoins
NOP

SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6

NOP

NOP

NOP
LI T1 2

NOP

NOP

NOP

LI S0 0 ; Item #1
leaveoffering:
ADDIU T1 S4 24 ; Item 1 Address
ADDU T1 S0 T1 ; Add choice index struct to get correct Item address
LI T0 0xFF ; No Item
SB T0 0(T1) ; Delete Item

JAL FixUpPlayerItemSlots
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index

JAL RefreshHUD
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index

Insert per frame hook.code:
; NAME: Insert per frame hook
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct

ADDIU SP SP -160
SW RA 156(SP)

LUI T0 hi(HookData)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(HookData)
LW V0 0(T0) ; Load HookData operation
LUI V1 0x8000 ; 0x8000000
ORI V1 V1 0xE7F0 ; 0x8000E7F0, address in main game loop
SW V0 0(V1) ; Insert rainhook to CustomCode in main game loop

;LUI T0 hi(HookData2)

.align 16
HookData: ; Rainhook to jump to CustomCode in main game loop
J CustomCode

.align 16
CustomCode:
ADDIU SP SP -120
SW A0 100(SP)
SW V0 96(SP)
SW S0 104(SP)
SW RA 116(SP)
SW T0 112(SP)
SW T1 108(SP)

LUI T0 0x800D ; 0x800D0000
LW T0 0xC3DC(T0) ; Load value from 0x800CC3DC
BEQZ T0 Skip ; If 0x800CC3DC == NULL (not in board play), skip
NOP
; else, run custom code here

LI T0 0x800CD0A7 ; Hidden Block Flag
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Load Flag value
BEQZ T1 everyoneisCPU ; exit if Hidden Blocks are hidden
NOP

LI T0 0x800D124F ; Star HB Address
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Star HB Space Index

JAL GetSpaceData ; at V0
MOVE A0 T1 

LI T0 0x3e051eb8 ; float for 1.3x space size
SW T0 20(V0) ; Increase Horizontal size
SW T0 28(V0) ; Increase Vertical size

LI T0 0x800CE1C5 ; Coin HB Address
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Coin HB Space Index

JAL GetSpaceData ; at V0
MOVE A0 T1 

LI T0 0x3e051eb8 ; float for 1.3x space size
SW T0 20(V0) ; Increase Horizontal size
SW T0 28(V0) ; Increase Vertical size

LI T0 0x800CC4E5 ; Item HB Address
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Item HB Space Index

JAL GetSpaceData ; at V0
MOVE A0 T1 

LI T0 0x3e051eb8 ; float for 1.3x space size
SW T0 20(V0) ; Increase Horizontal size
SW T0 28(V0) ; Increase Vertical size

LI T0 0x800CD0A4 ; Hidden Vlock Flag
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Load Flag value
BEQZ T1 everyoneisCPU ; exit if Hidden Blocks are hidden
NOP

JAL GetSpaceData ; at V0
MOVE A0 T1 

LI T0 0x3e051eb8 ; float for 1.3x space size
SW T0 20(V0) ; Increase Horizontal size
SW T0 28(V0) ; Increase Vertical size
;============================================================
everyoneisCPU:
LI T0 0x800CD0A5 ; Everyone is CPU Flag
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Load Flag value
BEQZ T1 Skip ; exit if effect isn't active
NOP
LI S0 0 ; Player 1
everyoneisCPUloop:
LI T1 4 
BEQ S0 T1 Skip ; exit once everyone is checked
NOP
LI T0 0x800CD0A6 ; Who is Human Flag
LBU T1 0(T0) ; Load Flag Value
LI T0 1 
SLLV T0 T0 S0 ; Shift by Player Index
AND T0 T0 T1 ; 1 if flag is on 
BEQL T0 R0 everyoneisCPUloop
ADDIU S0 S0 1 ; loop if player is a CPU

JAL GetPlayerStruct ; at V0
MOVE A0 S0 ; Player Index

SB R0 1(V0) ; Difficulty (Easy)
LI T1 5 ; CPU Index
SB T1 4(V0) ; Turn into CPU

J everyoneisCPUloop
ADDIU S0 S0 1 ; Add to check next player


Skip:
LW A0 100(SP)
LW V0 96(SP)
LW S0 104(SP)
LW RA 116(SP)
LW T0 112(SP)
LW T1 108(SP)
J 0x8000E7C0 ; Resume main game loop
ADDIU SP SP 120

Merged Path Fix (v2).code:
; NAME: Merged Path Fix (v2)
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: Space|Behind
; PARAM: Space|Next
; PARAM: Space|Check

ADDIU SP SP -52
SW RA 48(SP)
SW S4 44(SP)



JAL GetPlayerStruct ; at V0
LI A0 -1
MOVE S4 V0 ; Copy to S4

CheckChain:
LBU T1 21(S4) ; Previous Chain Index
LBU T2 22(S4) ; Previous ChainSpace Index
ADDIU T0 R0 Behind_chain_index
BNE T0 T1 CheckChain2
NOP
ADDIU T0 R0 Behind_chain_space_index
BNE T0 T2 CheckChain2
NOP
J SetupSpace
NOP

CheckChain2:
LBU T1 21(S4) ; Previous Chain Index
LBU T2 22(S4) ; Previous ChainSpace Index
ADDIU T0 R0 Check_chain_index
BEQ T0 T1 exit
NOP
ADDIU T0 R0 Check_chain_space_index
BEQ T0 T1 exit
NOP

SetupSpace:
LBU A0 29(S4) ; Assigns Current Player Index to A0
ADDIU A1 R0 Next_chain_index ; Assigns Chain Index to A1
ADDIU A2 R0 Next_chain_space_index ; Assigns Space Index to A2
JAL SetNextChainAndSpace 
NOP

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Assigns Current Player Index to A0
ADDIU A1 R0 Behind_chain_index ; Assigns Chain Index to A1
ADDIU A2 R0 Behind_chain_space_index ; Assigns Space Index to A2
JAL SetPrevChainAndSpace 
NOP



exit:
LW S4 44(SP)
LW RA 48(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 52

Reverse&Next Space Setup.code:
; NAME: Reverse&Next Space Setup
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: Space|Reverse
; PARAM: Space|Next

ADDIU SP SP -40
SW RA 36(SP)

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex ; Player Index located at V0
NOP
ADD A0 R0 V0 ; Assigns Current Player Index to A0
ADDIU A1 R0 Reverse_chain_index ; Assigns Chain Index to A1
ADDIU A2 R0 Reverse_chain_space_index ; Assigns Space Index to A2
JAL SetPrevChainAndSpace 
NOP

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex ; Player Index located at V0
NOP
ADD A0 R0 V0 ; Assigns Current Player Index to A0
ADDIU A1 R0 Next_chain_index ; Assigns Chain Index to A1
ADDIU A2 R0 Next_chain_space_index ; Assigns Space Index to A2
JAL SetNextChainAndSpace 
NOP

LW RA 36(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 40

[Junction 1] Dicey Junctions check.code:
; NAME: [Junction 1] Dicey Junctions check
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: Space|Left
; PARAM: Space|Right

ADDIU SP SP -80
SW RA 76(SP)
SW S4 72(SP)
SW S3 68(SP)
SW S2 64(SP)
SW S0 60(SP)

LI S0 0

JAL GetPlayerStruct
LI A0 -1
MOVE S4 V0 

LBU T4 23(S4) ; Status Flags
ANDI T0 T4 0x80 
BNEZ T0 exit ; exit if player is in reverse
NOP

LBU T0 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 T0 ; Shift Left by Player Index 

LUI S2 hi(0x800CD09A)
ADDIU S2 S2 lo(0x800CD09A) ; Dicey Junction Flag Address
LBU T4 0(S2) ; Flag Value

AND T1 T4 T2 ; Compare Flag Value to Player Index

LI S3 50 ; 50/50 
BNEZL T1 diceyjunctions ; Branch
LI S0 1 ; Flag for removing Dicey Junction Flag


JAL PlayerIsCPU
LI A0 -1 

BEQZ V0 exit ; If 0, exit because it's a human
NOP

LBU S3 1(S4) ; Load CPU's Difficulty (0-3)

J checkstar
NOP



LBU T1 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index

LUI T0 hi(0x800CD0A1)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(0x800CD0A1) ; Drink Count Address
ADDU T0 T0 T1 ; T0 now holds current player's drink count address
LBU T2 0(T0) ; T2 now holds current player's drink count value

SLTI T3 T2 4 ; ON IF Player has 3 or less drinks
BNEZ T3 LeftChoice
NOP

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayerHasCoins ; 
LI A1 20 ; Coins

BNEZ V0 checkstar ; Check Star Location if 20 Coins or more
NOP

checkspacesremaining:
LUI T0 hi(cur_player_spaces_remaining)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(cur_player_spaces_remaining) ; Address of spaces remaining
LW T0 0(T0) ; Load Value


LI T1 3
BEQ T0 T1 checkitems
NOP
LI T1 7
BEQ T0 T1 checkfor20coins
NOP
LI T1 9
BEQ T0 T1 checkfor0coins
NOP
J exit
NOP

checkstar:
LUI T0 hi(current_star_spawn)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(current_star_spawn) ; Address of current Star Spawn Cycle
ADDIU T1 T0 1 ; Address of first Star Spawn Index in the Cycle
LBU T0 0(T0) ; Load Index of Star Spawn to T0
ADDU T0 T0 T1 ; Add to get address of current Star Spawn Index
LBU T2 0(T0) ; Load current Star Spawn Index to T2

LI T9 0
BEQ T2 T9 RightChoice ; Branch IF it's Star 00
NOP
J exit
NOP

checkbank:
LUI T0 hi(bank_coin_total)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(bank_coin_total) ; Address of current bank total
LH T0 0(T0) ; Load Value

SLTI T1 T0 10 ; ON IF Bank has less than 10 coins
BNEZ T1 RightChoice
NOP
J LeftChoice
NOP

checkitems:
JAL PlayerHasEmptyItemSlot
LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
LUI T1 hi(0xFFFFFFFF)
ADDIU T1 T1 lo(0xFFFFFFFF) ; No Item Value
BNE V0 T1 LeftChoice ; Left if full
NOP
J checkbank
NOP

checkfor20coins:
LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayerHasCoins
LI A1 20

BEQZ V0 LeftChoice ; Pick Left if no coins 
NOP
J RightChoice
NOP

checkfor0coins:
LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayerHasCoins
LI A1 1

BEQZ V0 RightChoice ; Pick Left if no coins 
NOP
J LeftChoice
NOP

LeftChoice:
BEQZ S3 CalculateChance
LI A0 50 ; 50%
LI T9 1 ; Normal Difficulty
BEQ S3 T9 CalculateChance
LI A0 30 ; 30%
LI T9 2 ; Hard Difficulty
BEQ S3 T9 CalculateChance
LI A0 3 ; 3%
J CalculateChance
LI A0 0 ; 0% Super Hard Difficulty

RightChoice:
BEQZ S3 CalculateChance
LI A0 50 ; 50%
LI T9 1 ; Normal Difficulty
BEQ S3 T9 CalculateChance
LI A0 70 ; 70%
LI T9 2 ; Hard Difficulty
BEQ S3 T9 CalculateChance
LI A0 97 ; 97%

LI A0 100 ; 100% Super Hard Difficulty 
J CalculateChance
NOP

diceyjunctions:
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 4 ; Dizzy Animation
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A2 2 ; Don't loop

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0xC2 ; Dizzy Sound effect

LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayVoice
LI A1 1 ; Sad Voice

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 45 ; Frames


CalculateChance:
JAL RNGPercentChance ; 0 = Left - 1 = Right
NOP 

BNEZ V0 GoRight
NOP

LI A1 Left_chain_index
J SetDecision
LI A2 Left_chain_space_index

GoRight:
LI A1 Right_chain_index
LI A2 Right_chain_space_index

SetDecision:
JAL SetNextChainAndSpace
LBU A0 29(S4)

BEQZ S0 exit
NOP

LBU T0 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 T0 ; Shift Left by Player Index 
LBU T4 0(S2) ; Flag Value

SUBU T4 T4 T2 ; Subtract
SB T4 0(S2) ; Store new Flag Value


exit:
LW S0 60(SP)
LW S2 64(SP)
LW S3 68(SP)
LW S4 72(SP)
LW RA 76(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80

.align 16
; A0 = Player's Index
; A1 = Happy/Sad Index
PlayVoice:
ADDIU SP SP -32
SW RA 28(SP)

JAL GetPlayerStruct
NOP

LBU T0 3(V0) ; Character Index

BNEZ A1 sad
NOP

happy:
JAL PlaySound
ADDIU A0 T0 0x275 ; Mario's Happy Voice Index
J PlayVoice_exit
NOP

sad:
JAL PlaySound
ADDIU A0 T0 0x287

PlayVoice_exit:
LW RA 28(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 32

LBU T1 29(S4) ; Current Player's Index

LUI T0 hi(0x800CD0A1)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(0x800CD0A1) ; Drink Count Address
ADDU T0 T0 T1 ; T0 now holds current player's drink count address
LBU T2 0(T0) ; T2 now holds current player's drink count value

SLTI T3 T2 4 ; ON IF Player has 3 or less drinks
BNEZ T3 LeftChoice
NOP

LBU A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayerHasCoins ; 
LI A1 20 ; Coins

BNEZ V0 checkstar ; Check Star Location if 20 Coins or more
NOP

checkspacesremaining:
LUI T0 hi(cur_player_spaces_remaining)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(cur_player_spaces_remaining) ; Address of spaces remaining
LW T0 0(T0) ; Load Value


LI T1 3
BEQ T0 T1 checkitems
NOP
LI T1 7
BEQ T0 T1 checkfor20coins
NOP
LI T1 9
BEQ T0 T1 checkfor0coins
NOP
J exit
NOP

checkstar:
LUI T0 hi(current_star_spawn)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(current_star_spawn) ; Address of current Star Spawn Cycle
ADDIU T1 T0 1 ; Address of first Star Spawn Index in the Cycle
LBU T0 0(T0) ; Load Index of Star Spawn to T0
ADDU T0 T0 T1 ; Add to get address of current Star Spawn Index
LBU T2 0(T0) ; Load current Star Spawn Index to T2

LI T9 3
BEQ T2 T9 LeftChoice ; Branch IF it's Star 03
NOP

J exit
NOP

checkbank:
LUI T0 hi(bank_coin_total)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(bank_coin_total) ; Address of current bank total
LH T0 0(T0) ; Load Value

SLTI T1 T0 10 ; ON IF Bank has less than 10 coins
BNEZ T1 RightChoice
NOP
J LeftChoice
NOP

checkitems:
JAL PlayerHasEmptyItemSlot
LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
LUI T1 hi(0xFFFFFFFF)
ADDIU T1 T1 lo(0xFFFFFFFF) ; No Item Value
BNE V0 T1 LeftChoice ; Left if full
NOP
J checkbank
NOP

checkfor20coins:
LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayerHasCoins
LI A1 20

BEQZ V0 LeftChoice ; Pick Left if no coins 
NOP
J RightChoice
NOP

checkfor0coins:
LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayerHasCoins
LI A1 1

BEQZ V0 RightChoice ; Pick Left if no coins 
NOP
J LeftChoice
NOP

LeftChoice:
BEQZ S3 CalculateChance
LI A0 50 ; 50%
LI T9 1 ; Normal Difficulty
BEQ S3 T9 CalculateChance
LI A0 30 ; 30%
LI T9 2 ; Hard Difficulty
BEQ S3 T9 CalculateChance
LI A0 3 ; 3%
J CalculateChance
LI A0 0 ; 0% Super Hard Difficulty

RightChoice:
BEQZ S3 CalculateChance
LI A0 50 ; 50%
LI T9 1 ; Normal Difficulty
BEQ S3 T9 CalculateChance
LI A0 70 ; 70%
LI T9 2 ; Hard Difficulty
BEQ S3 T9 CalculateChance
LI A0 97 ; 97%

LI A0 100 ; 100% Super Hard Difficulty 
J CalculateChance
NOP

diceyjunctions:
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 4 ; Dizzy Animation
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A2 2 ; Don't loop

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0xC2 ; Dizzy Sound effect

LB A0 29(S4) ; Player Index
JAL PlayVoice
LI A1 1 ; Sad Voice

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 45 ; Frames


CalculateChance:
JAL RNGPercentChance ; 0 = Left - 1 = Right
NOP 

BNEZ V0 GoRight
NOP

LI A1 Left_chain_index
J SetDecision
LI A2 Left_chain_space_index

GoRight:
LI A1 Right_chain_index
LI A2 Right_chain_space_index

SetDecision:
JAL SetNextChainAndSpace
LBU A0 29(S4)

BEQZ S0 exit
NOP

LBU T0 29(S4) ; Current Player Index
LI T1 1 
SLLV T2 T1 T0 ; Shift Left by Player Index 
LBU T4 0(S2) ; Flag Value

SUBU T4 T4 T2 ; Subtract
SB T4 0(S2) ; Store new Flag Value


exit:
LW S0 60(SP)
LW S2 64(SP)
LW S3 68(SP)
LW S4 72(SP)
LW RA 76(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80

.align 16
; A0 = Player's Index
; A1 = Happy/Sad Index
PlayVoice:
ADDIU SP SP -32
SW RA 28(SP)

JAL GetPlayerStruct
NOP

LBU T0 3(V0) ; Character Index

BNEZ A1 sad
NOP

happy:
JAL PlaySound
ADDIU A0 T0 0x275 ; Mario's Happy Voice Index
J PlayVoice_exit
NOP

sad:
JAL PlaySound
ADDIU A0 T0 0x287

PlayVoice_exit:
LW RA 28(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 32

audioSelectCode.code:
; Customize the background music used each turn!
; This function runs whenever the board music starts playing.
; Custom tracks you've added are available as MUSIC_TRACK_INDEX_#,
; e.g. MUSIC_TRACK_INDEX_1 for the first added custom song.
; (If you aren't using custom music, then only MUSIC_TRACK_INDEX_1
; exists and it is set to the in-game music index you chose.)
ADDIU SP SP -80
SW RA 76(SP)

LUI T0 hi(total_turns)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(total_turns)
LBU T1 0(T0) 

LUI T0 hi(current_turn)
ADDIU T0 T0 lo(current_turn)
LBU T2 0(T0)

SUBU T3 T1 T2 ; Subtract current turn from total turns
SLTI T0 T3 5 ; ON if 0-4 (Turn 16-20)
BEQL T0 r0 exit ; 
LI V0 MUSIC_TRACK_INDEX_1

LI V0 MUSIC_TRACK_INDEX_2


exit:
LW RA 76(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80
